('9e1b88dd-eb62-4427-ae94-3fde6218713c','Blanka','Stand MP','','5MP','normal',10,3,15,-4,3,700,'H','su','Good poke tool with strong hitbox priority',2,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('e156ca3d-ebcf-4377-9aef-becfcde3f21f','Blanka','Stand HP','','5HP','normal',10,7,17,-3,3,800,'H','sp, su','Mostly a combo tool (hitboxes not ideal for poking or anti-airing); Forces stand; Last 2 active frames whiff on grounded opponents (only hits the air above Blanka); +5F extra recovery frames (22F) on whiff',3,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('a5225476-ada3-4748-abcb-941d567d1093','Blanka','Stand LK','','5LK','normal',4,4,7,-2,5,300,'H','ch, sp, su','Blanka''s fastest normal at 4F; Chains into stand LK / crouch LP / crouch LK; Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo',4,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('4a80b50e-eb32-495d-9c14-674277041ab4','Blanka','Stand MK','','5MK','normal',8,3,17,-2,4,600,'H','sp, su','+3F more recovery (20F) on whiff',5,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('1b59edb0-fc1b-4e71-b105-1af138a01775','Blanka','Stand HK','','5HK','normal',7,9,18,-4,6,800,'H','','Forces stand; Combo tool as well as a solid anti-air on later active frames and also a good oki / meaty tool; Launches airborne opponents into a limited juggle state on Counter-Hit / Punish Counter; Active frames 7-9 can hit cross-up (behind Blanka) unlike most anti-air tools in the game; The brief extended leg hurtbox on frame 6 of start-up (1F before active) is strike invincible (cannot counter-poke projectiles); 3F fewer recovery frames (15F) on block/parry',6,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('fbbdcfe6-3419-42c8-97f7-fbfd97966f9b','Blanka','Crouch LP','','2LP','normal',6,3,8,-2,5,300,'H','ch, sp, su','Far range cancelable jab (furthest range of Blanka''s light buttons); Chains into stand LK / crouch LP / crouch LK; Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo',7,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('12204ac9-ee43-476b-b73d-67c0a75387b2','Blanka','Crouch MP','','2MP','normal',9,5,16,-5,-1,600,'H','sp, su','Very far range cancelable medium that''s also a situational anti-air (but cannot hit cross-up); Solid poke / buffer tool with very lenient cancel window making this very easy to hit confirm (19F hit confirm window); Can hit on later active frames when spaced out, increasing frame advantage but also making it slightly harder to hit confirm',8,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('1a22a8e4-97ed-4606-bfff-2753b409772f','Blanka','Crouch HP','','2HP','normal',15,5,20,-5,0,900,'H','','Forces stand; Very far range poke that can also anti-air in specific situations; The brief extended punch hurtbox on frame 14 of start-up (1F before active) is strike invincible (cannot counter-poke projectiles); Puts airborne opponents into a limited juggle state on Punish Counter; +1F extra recovery frames (21F) on block',9,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('256713a6-7bc7-497c-9544-b66067956069','Blanka','Crouch LK','','2LK','normal',5,2,10,-3,3,200,'L','ch','Chains into stand LK / crouch LP / crouch LK; Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo',10,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('93ed34b9-14ad-45e8-89c7-610638419888','Blanka','Crouch MK','','2MK','normal',8,3,16,-5,5,500,'L','sp, su','Good frame advantage on hit for a cancelable crouch MK (can be used as a combo tool); +2F extra recovery frames (18F) on whiff; Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo',11,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
