('7b5e4e14-abd2-416d-b609-5ac890dcddb9','C.Viper','Stand LK','','5LK','normal',5,3,11,-2,3,300,'H','sj, sp, su','Primary 5F punish tool and link option after chained light normals (can link after Crouch LP in 4-hit light confirms); Higher hitstun than other light normals (combos naturally into MP Thunder Dash); Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo',4,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('39933d71-0d01-42e0-b8fa-548e50adf902','C.Viper','Stand MK','','5MK','normal',8,3,18,-3,4,700,'H','sj','+2F extra recovery frames (20F) on whiff; Strong poke and whiff punish tool that can be Super Jump canceled for more damage',5,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('ec1e92e0-d56a-4f96-a55a-59d91475d630','C.Viper','Stand HK','','5HK','normal',10,4,20,-3,4,900,'H','sj','Puts airborne opponents into an OTG juggle state on hit; Stagger state on Punish Counter (+19); Shorter range against crouching opponents; Can be juggled into after Seismo + SJC Air Burn Kick, then Super Jump canceled for further damage (SJC into grounded OD Burn Kick is a 2F timing window that''s part of many optimal combo routes); Punish Counter advantage is big enough to allow for a Super Jump cancel into a full jump-in combo',6,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('c10fe9e5-cb92-4057-996e-fcad7ad7d80c','C.Viper','Crouch LP','','2LP','normal',4,3,8,-1,5,300,'H','ch, sj, sp, su','Chains into stand LP / crouch LP / crouch LK; Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo; Topmost hurtboxes on frames 1-6 are vulnerable only to airborne attacks (this is to discourage its use as an anti-air); 1F extra hitstun (and frame advantage) than stand LP but has less range; Can be used as the third hit of a chain that links into stand LK, but this will whiff if the opponent stand blocks (also whiffs under many reversal standing jabs at this range)',7,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
