('4eb4ef6a-11c3-400b-8313-a63122c69e78','Cammy','Stand MK','','5MK','normal',8,3,18,-4,3,700,'H','','Mostly a poke tool; Cammy lifts up her front leg hurtbox on frames 7-10 making this a solid tool against low attacks',5,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('dc4eb5d2-94f5-4316-a618-e04b6a1c8cdd','Cammy','Stand HK','','5HK','normal',11,3,19,-3,2,900,'H','','Good range poke tool as well as horizontal anti-air; Knockdown on Punish Counter leads to great corner carry (but no follow-up juggle); +2F extra recovery frames (21F) on whiff; The brief extended leg hurtbox on frame 10 of start-up (1F before active) is strike invincible (cannot counter-poke projectiles)',6,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
