('726996c3-fe83-4e16-a84b-10bd2ca0de69','Cammy','LK Cannon Spike','','623LK','special',5,12,24,-36,NULL,900,'H','su3','Invincible to airborne attacks on frames 1-14; Airborne on frames 7-40 (Forced Knockdown state); Deals 100 less damage (800) on active frames 3-12; Cannot hit cross-up (behind Cammy); Shortest horizontal distance (good for close range anti-air); Opponent is launched too high for Level 3 Super to combo when canceled',37,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('a8589d94-22a7-4f6e-a6f2-3534d3bccced','Cammy','MK Cannon Spike','','623MK','special',6,12,25,-36,NULL,1000,'H','su3','Invincible to airborne attacks on frames 1-9; Airborne on frames 8-42 (Forced Knockdown state); Cannot hit cross-up (behind Cammy); Deals 200 less damage (800) on active frames 3-12; Medium horizontal distance (useful all-purpose anti-air); Opponent is launched too high for Level 3 Super to combo when canceled',38,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
