('f93227d7-f413-421d-a9ef-06fd8cb867c2','Cammy','OD Hooligan Combination','','236PP','special',20,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','Airborne on frames 7-40 (Forced Knockdown state); Lower body Projectile invincible on frames 7-40; Trajectory depends on button combinations (LP+MP = LP | LP+HP = MP | MP+HP=HP); Cancelable into enhanced OD follow-ups on frames 20-40',50,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
