('fddf133b-6eab-4a02-8d85-615f35f414ce','Cammy','Killer Bee Spin','','214214P','super',13,9,37,-24,NULL,3000,'H','','Armor Break; Weaker non-cinematic version occurs on hit against airborne opponents (~KD +70 and allows follow-up juggles); Depletes 1 Drive Bar on hit for the opponent; Despite not being properly invincible, this move can still be used to blow through oki / offense since Cammy''s hurtboxes are displaced into the air during the screen freeze, however this is extremely risky to do due to the slow start-up',67,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('a98a90b0-f046-49e2-82b6-1ccfa09a0080','Cammy','Aerial Killer Bee Spin','','214214P (air)','super',13,NULL,37,-23,NULL,3000,'H','','Armor Break; Weaker non-cinematic version occurs on hit against airborne opponents (~KD +70 and allows follow-up juggles); Can only be performed during a forward jump; Depletes 1 Drive Bar on hit for the opponent',68,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('2f818948-6a3e-48a8-bdb5-81c4edc19cef','Cammy','Delta Red Assault','','236236P','super',9,15,38,-33,NULL,4000,'H','','Fully invincible on frames 1-13; Airborne on frames 9-27; Armor Break; Depletes 1.5 Drive Bars on hit for the opponent; Super cinematic time regenerates ~1.9 Drive Bars for Cammy; Full-screen range and fast start-up makes this a really threatening tool in neutral when Cammy has SA3 ready; Can lose or trade against slow projectiles when used from full screen; Can trade on active frames 14-23 (runs out of invincibility) dealing only 500 damage since it doesn''t transition into the cinematic version',69,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('f98a58ef-b23c-4c46-8bc6-f365617d7e66','Cammy','Delta Red Assault (Critical Art)','','236236P (CA)','super',9,15,38,-33,NULL,4500,'H','','Fully invincible on frames 1-13; Airborne on frames 9-27; Armor Break; Critical Art does +500 extra damage over regular version; Depletes 2 Drive Bars on hit for the opponent; Super cinematic time regenerates ~1.9 Drive Bars for Cammy; Full-screen range and fast start-up makes this a really threatening tool in neutral when Cammy has SA3 ready; Can lose or trade against slow projectiles when used from full screen; Can trade on active frames 14-23 (runs out of invincibility) dealing only 500 damage since it doesn''t transition into the cinematic version',70,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('13a00f69-6ae4-4d50-a8ef-fcb06beb972e','Chun-Li','Stand LP','','5LP','normal',4,3,7,-3,5,300,'H','ch, ss, sp, su','Chains into stand LP / crouch LP / crouch LK; Combos naturally into stand MP; Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo; Long range for a jab',1,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('458d8d36-d587-40f4-bd72-063baa9bd19a','Chun-Li','Stand MP','','5MP','normal',5,4,10,1,6,600,'H','ss, sp, su','Short range combo / frametrap tool',2,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('42b1750d-30b9-4efe-8190-f8ab747d87f9','Chun-Li','Stand HP','','5HP','normal',13,3,20,-3,2,800,'H','ss','Amazing neutral / whiff punish tool; Cancelable into Serenity Stream (Crouch Stance) and can perform stance follow-ups after 16F (much worse frame advantage noted in parantheses if you don''t immediately do a follow-up from the stance); Winning footsies since 1992',3,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('8cb8fa5b-14e1-4196-8512-1a60f7b1346b','Chun-Li','Stand LK','','5LK','normal',5,3,10,-2,2,300,'H','ss, sp, su','Decent range combo tool; Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo',4,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('d44a1081-8657-48d5-b92a-872b07d0c936','Chun-Li','Stand MK','','5MK','normal',7,4,16,-2,4,500,'H','ss, sp, su','Cannot hit crouching; Solid anti-air; Cannot hit cross-up (behind Chun-Li)',5,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('d2daea19-753f-461a-8f35-7c3ece664937','Chun-Li','Stand HK','','5HK','normal',14,3,18,0,4,900,'H','ss','Cannot hit crouching; Mid range horizontal anti-air; Extended leg and head hurtbox are invincible to airborne strikes on frames 14-16; Cannot hit cross-up (behind Chun-Li); Puts airborne opponents into a limited juggle state on hit (free juggle state on Punish Counter); Incurs a 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo; Cancelable into Serenity Stream (Crouch Stance) with 12F start-up (much worse frame advantage noted in parantheses if you don''t immediately do a follow-up from the stance)',6,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('c1bef920-7f85-41b9-8836-e251f44b4f61','Chun-Li','Crouch LP','','2LP','normal',4,3,7,-2,4,300,'H','ch, ss, sp, su','Chains into stand LP / crouch LP / crouch LK; Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo',7,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('3a79456a-199d-45cd-85aa-6910731c70a1','Chun-Li','Crouch MP','','2MP','normal',6,4,13,-2,4,600,'H','ss, sp, su','Decent range and disjointed for a poke; +1F extra recovery (14F) on whiff; Topmost hurtboxes on frames 1-9 are vulnerable only to airborne attacks (this is to discourage its use as an anti-air)',8,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('7af718b3-7bc9-4d74-8449-ea6445b4ec66','Chun-Li','Crouch HP','','2HP','normal',11,3,18,-3,1,900,'H','ss, sp, su','Forces stand; Only cancelable on the second hit; Solid anti-air on frames 12-13 and again on frames 21-23; Cannot hit cross-up (behind Chun-Li); Carries over Counter-Hit / Punish Counter bonus frame advantage to both hits; First hit puts airborne opponents into a limited juggle state (second hit air resets them, but can whiff in certain scenarios); Cancelable into Serenity Stream (Crouch Stance) with 11F start-up (much worse frame advantage noted in parantheses if you don''t immediately do a follow-up from the stance)',9,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('d8151cdf-118b-49cd-9d4f-9f8e5885f5c7','Chun-Li','Crouch LK','','2LK','normal',4,2,10,-2,0,200,'L','ch, ss, sp, su','Special cancelable (unlike most other crouch LKs); Chains into stand LP / crouch LP / crouch LK; Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo',10,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('ae505f04-6735-405b-b8ff-3ca4541911c5','Chun-Li','Crouch MK','','2MK','normal',7,3,19,-6,-2,500,'L','ss, sp, su','Good start-up and range low poke and combo tool; Incurs a 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo',11,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('da3ef246-68a1-440d-8526-f4844a4dda54','Chun-Li','Crouch HK','','2HK','normal',9,6,19,-9,NULL,900,'L','ss','Cancelable into Serenity Stream (Crouch Stance) with 23F start-up (much worse frame advantage noted in parantheses if you don''t immediately do a follow-up from the stance); Knockdown advantage when canceling into Serenity Stream (Crouch Stance) depends on what Chun-Li does afterwards: Remain in Crouch Stance: +36 KD | Exiting stance manually early (inputting QCB+P again): +13 KD (+17 KD if you cancel the stance exit early into other moves) | -8 KD (punishable) if Chun-Li doesn''t remain in Crouch Stance or exit it manually early (inputting QCB+P again); Has more active frames than most sweeps (can be as safe as -4 with meaty timing)',12,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
