('53714133-c3ab-44c8-8ada-6bcd14be30a0','Chun-Li','Wall Jump','','9 during jump near wall','unique',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','Forced Knockdown and Counter-Hit state for the entire duration of the jump; Can be performed after any jump direction as long as the wall is in range',20,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('7b566a8d-283d-4a09-9e16-0bcfaf3657ba','Chun-Li','Yoso Kick','','2MK (air)','normal',3,11,NULL,NULL,NULL,300,'H','sp, su, tc','Not an Overhead; All 3 hits can cross-up; Puts airborne opponents into a juggle state; Cancelable into airborne Lighting Kicks and Level 1 Super; Can be canceled into other air normals as well; Forced Knockdown state after the bounce on Hit / Block; First stomp incurs a 15% damage scaling when hit as the start of a combo',21,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('652f7e37-e2ac-41f2-ba04-f7b1db3a33bc','Chun-Li','Soaring Eagle Punches','','8HP > 8HP','normal',16,4,NULL,12,17,500,'M','','Puts airborne opponents into a juggle state; Target combo can be performed on whiff; Huge hitstun/blockstun against grounded opponents on the 2nd hit, allowing for unique follow-up combos / blockstring pressure that is normally impossible after a jump-in normal',22,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
