('3531f6cf-8d42-47fa-b2b2-fd74e2f53651','Chun-Li','OD Aerial Hundred Lightning Kicks','','236KK(air)','special',6,2,5,-26,NULL,1600,'H','','6 hits; Only possible during neutral or forward jump; Can Tiger Knee motion this to do it closer to the ground (this also makes it only -1 on stand block); Whiffs on crouching; Crouching state during the 5F landing recovery (only 3F landing recovery on HIT); Recovery frames listed refers to the landing recovery frames (not including the variable air time); Knockdown advantage listed on hit refers to when hitting a standing grounded opponent (with Tiger Knee motion input style) - the KDA varies greatly when hitting airborne opponents (usually even higher KDA then); Puts the opponent into a limited juggle state on hit; Forced Knockdown state while airborne',55,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('41143e4a-13c6-47f3-bd2c-45fd37dabec3','Chun-Li','LK Spinning Bird Kick','','28LK','special',9,2,6,-18,NULL,1000,'H','','Takes 30 frames to charge; Airborne on frames 8-32 (Forced Knockdown state); Does not require charge if canceled into from Stance moves',56,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('84273184-1841-40cf-976d-3755c2ed087c','Chun-Li','MK Spinning Bird Kick','','28MK','special',16,2,8,-17,NULL,1200,'H','','Takes 30 frames to charge; Airborne on frames 15-56 (Forced Knockdown state); Does not require charge if canceled into from Stance moves',57,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
