('d2b7b0d9-7c9c-4d05-b873-9a586e45c212','Chun-Li','OD Tenshokyaku','','22KK','special',6,3,16,-40,NULL,1400,'H','','Fully invincible frames 1-7; Airborne on frames 8-32 (Forced Knockdown state); Cannot hit cross-up (behind Chun-Li); Active and Recovery frames listed refers to the version that plays out on Block and Whiff (only does the follow-up attacks on hit); Chun-Li is in a crouching state during the final recovery frame',67,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('6a3a8f07-9e10-432e-b0e9-b25168506321','Chun-Li','Kikosho','','236236P','super',7,70,46,-22,NULL,1700,'H','','Strike and Throw invincible on frames 1-7; 5-hit Super projectile; Armor Break; Depletes 0.5 Drive Bar on hit for the opponent; Can hit cross-up (behind Chun-Li); Minimum damage scaling of 30%',68,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('b5c6fb5f-5b87-4086-a04f-f53f17d274e7','Chun-Li','Aerial Kikosho','','236236P (air)','super',7,50,NULL,-20,NULL,2000,'H','','Strike and Throw invincible on frame 1 only (during screen freeze); 5-hit Super projectile; 16F landing recovery frames (total recovery frames vary depending on how high from the ground the Super was performed); Armor Break; Depletes 0.5 Drive Bar on hit for the opponent; Can hit cross-up (behind Chun-Li); Minimum damage scaling of 30%',69,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('0eb623dd-0902-499b-bc76-4b71d4983059','Chun-Li','Hoyoku-sen','','236236K','super',11,2,48,-35,NULL,2000,'H','j','Fully invincible frames 1-12; Last hit is jump cancelable by holding up (Chun-Li always jumps forward); Armor Break; Depletes 1 Drive Bar on hit for the opponent; Minimum damage scaling of 40%; Launches the opponent into a free juggle state on hit (or maintains the current juggle state); Incurs a 40% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo; Counts as 3 hits of damage scaling when combo''d into; 30% penalty to Super meter gain on any of the follow-up hits she combos into after this move',70,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('25b14f04-3382-42cf-8d27-681d0acaac1a','Chun-Li','Soten Ranka','','214214K','super',8,2,40,-24,NULL,4000,'H','','Fully invincible frames 1-9; No cinematic if the first hit whiffs (the following 2 hits on whiff do 1000 damage together); Armor Break; Depletes 1.5 Drive Bars on hit for the opponent; Super cinematic time regenerates ~1.8 Drive Bars for Chun-Li; Minimum damage scaling of 50%; Incurs 10% damage scaling when canceled into from specials',71,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('30d9b080-be56-4c8e-8a05-5ef08cc8845b','Chun-Li','Soten Ranka (Critical Art)','','214214K (CA)','super',8,2,40,-24,NULL,4500,'H','','Fully invincible frames 1-9; Critical Art does +500 damage over regular version; No cinematic if the first hit whiffs (the following 2 hits on whiff do 1000 damage together); Armor Break; Depletes 2 Drive Bars on hit for the opponent; Super cinematic time regenerates ~2 Drive Bars for Chun-Li; Minimum damage scaling of 50%; Incurs 10% damage scaling when canceled into from specials',72,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('9c2a510d-0273-44be-966b-15ee95352e50','Dee Jay','Stand LP','','5LP','normal',4,3,6,-1,4,300,'H','ch, sp, su, tc','Chains into stand LP / crouch LP / crouch LK; Fastest jab check in the game with barely any recovery frames makes this the safest meaty jab oki there is; Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo',1,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('0b3afbbc-9045-440d-9730-1fbc783ab615','Dee Jay','Stand MP','','5MP','normal',7,3,13,2,5,600,'H','tc','Good combo and frametrap tool that can also go into two different target combos',2,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('ce559bf6-e56d-44ff-9ed6-2c6a0f871615','Dee Jay','Stand HP','','5HP','normal',9,6,18,-4,3,800,'H','sp, su','Forces stand on active frames 1-2 (vital for his Jackknife Maximum combo routes); Strong combo / whiff punish tool with great range and lots of active frames (can easily convert into combos if spaced properly); Situational anti-air when used at range; Active frames 3-6 whiff on crouching opponents (don''t try to use this against crouching opponents from further away); Only cancelable on the first 2 active frames and deals 100 less damage (700) on active frames 3-6; Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo',3,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('e7190eab-e639-4aab-b4ef-fdda3a9f2d94','Dee Jay','Stand LK','','5LK','normal',5,2,12,-2,2,300,'H','sp, su','DJs only light button that combos into HK Sobat on hit and into OD Sobat in Punish situations, making this a good buffer tool; Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo',4,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('85793df4-c771-4154-96a6-d1cf5dbd8bd1','Dee Jay','Stand MK','','5MK','normal',9,3,16,-1,6,600,'H','','Combo starter as well as a decent poke tool',5,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('b8ff461d-1e6a-4278-ae68-a17def354a3b','Dee Jay','Stand HK','','5HK','normal',12,3,22,-5,1,800,'H','','Good range poke and whiff punish tool that leads to Drive Rush combos on Punish Counter; Puts airborne opponents into a limited juggle state on Punish Counter; The brief extended leg hurtbox on frame 11 of start-up (1F before active) is strike invincible (cannot counter-poke projectiles); +4F extra recovery frames (26F) on whiff; Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo',6,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('6f87ca5f-f92a-47fc-b363-c60a36314d19','Dee Jay','Crouch LP','','2LP','normal',5,3,8,-1,4,300,'H','ch, sp, su','Chains into stand LP / crouch LP / crouch LK; Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo; Topmost hurtboxes on frames 1-7 are vulnerable only to airborne attacks (this is to discourage its use as an anti-air)',7,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('f4a869d8-ef90-46f4-afe5-160f00d979c4','Dee Jay','Crouch MP','','2MP','normal',6,4,14,-1,4,600,'H','sp, su','Core buffer / combo tool and also applicable in a lot of oki / meaty situations; Has very good hitbox priority against low attacks; Fully cancelable and hit confirmable (19F hit confirm window) makes this Dee Jay''s best buffer tool in neutral',8,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('384dd341-44ae-4424-b2a6-a7b34f20fb8d','Dee Jay','Crouch HP','','2HP','normal',8,2,20,-2,6,800,'H','','Combo tool and a decent counterpoke with good hitbox priority; Forces stand (vital for his Jackknife Maximum combo routes); Puts airborne opponents into a limited juggle state on Punish Counter (and results in a +71~74 Hard Knockdown)',9,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('9212f12a-70b1-4e75-a14f-b541df2675d0','Dee Jay','Crouch LK','','2LK','normal',5,2,10,-2,2,200,'L','ch','Chains into stand LP / crouch LP / crouch LK; Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo',10,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('4b07309d-7cb1-4f29-9c8a-a69e49f47742','Dee Jay','Crouch MK','','2MK','normal',8,4,19,-6,NULL,700,'L','','Unorthodox sweep that only causes Hard Knockdown on Punish Counter; Good hitbox priority for a low attack; Can be very hard to punish on block for some characters even when used up close',11,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('b8aadf66-e8d6-4efe-bb74-5c3b3e0937a5','Dee Jay','Crouch HK','','2HK','normal',14,10,15,-11,NULL,900,'L','','Upper body and legs are invincible to airborne strikes on frames 12-23; Solid anti-air (but slow start-up); Puts airborne opponents into a limited juggle state (better juggle scenarios on Counter Hit and Punish)',12,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('6f7498d9-ee74-4e28-ab0e-c983692c462a','Dee Jay','Jump LP','','8LP','normal',4,7,NULL,0,4,300,'M','','Can be used as an instant Overhead',13,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('b3cdd250-2bdd-4907-ac2e-ba3f6926fed6','Dee Jay','Jump MP','','8MP','normal',6,4,NULL,6,10,700,'M','tc','Puts airborne opponents into a limited juggle state; Very lenient cancel window (25F) for the follow-up HP air target combo; Shifts the normal jumping hurtbox upward during start-up (helps with avoiding some attacks)',14,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('ac54662a-9a88-42f4-bc5b-1d5c95861e76','Dee Jay','Jump HP','','8HP','normal',9,6,NULL,4,8,800,'M','','Spikes down airborne opponents on hit',15,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('e6ed74c5-b6b4-4f6e-ae22-d7c59dd64ae1','Dee Jay','Jump LK','','8LK','normal',4,6,NULL,2,6,300,'M','','Situational air-to-air',16,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
