('dc0296d2-f886-4f08-9a43-e48e9f75a763','Dhalsim','Crouch HP','','2HP','normal',19,4,20,-8,3,800,'L','','Low attack; Low profiles on frames 11-46 (until fully recovered); Projectile invincible on upper body on frames 11-39; +4F extra recovery frames (24F) on whiff and Perfect Parry (Low); Useful to snipe under and punish most fireballs; Has natural juggle potential without Drive Rush (Juggle Limit: 2)',9,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
