('82497f4e-3b0e-4513-b403-825107b2fa27','Honda','OD Teppo Double Slap','','236KK > P','special',13,3,17,3,3,800,'H','su2, su3','Forward moving special that leaves Honda up close for mixups / pressure on hit or block; Puts airborne opponents into a limited juggle state on hit; Always leaves Honda in range for an Oicho Throw mixup if both hits are blocked; Very disjointed hitbox on the slaps, making it a useful approach tool',55,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
