('aa96d0fa-4b7f-4487-a23c-b94ab0758e21','Ed','Crouch MP','','2MP','normal',8,3,19,-6,2,500,'L','sp, su','Hits low (functions like other characters'' crouch MK); A little bit stubby compared to most crouch MK; Incurs a 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo',8,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
