('71ec9357-ec32-45b8-bf5f-e334b21cf159','Elena','HP Moon Glider','','214HP','special',28,3,20,-2,2,800,'H','su3','Very evasive tool that''s safe on block and grants follow-up combos on whiff punish (Punish Counter); Elena sways back quite a lot on frames 5-23 (reaches maximum sway back distance on frames 14-16); Maximum sway back distance: 0.71; Puts airborne opponents into a limited juggle state',67,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('8de74b1d-1457-4fa4-93ab-67aa8b832e88','Elena','Moon Glider Follow-up','','214P > 6P','special',16,2,25,-13,NULL,1400,'H','su3','Follow-up option from the Moon Glider sway that''s hit confirmable (18F window); Puts the opponent into a limited juggle state on hit (can only really extend the combo by canceling into SA3 / CA)',68,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('c8f20a90-b06c-42eb-af4a-b06b61197f9a','Elena','OD Moon Glider','','214PP','special',23,3,20,-3,1,800,'H','su2, su3','Evasive tool that''s safe on block and grants follow-up combos on whiff punish (Punish Counter); Elena sways back on frames 5-19 (reaches maximum sway back distance on frame 9; Maximum sway back distance: 0.56; Puts airborne opponents into a limited juggle state',69,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('ccd92421-d040-44e0-993b-9c2bcf67dde5','Elena','OD Moon Glider Follow-up','','214PP > 6P','special',16,2,35,-19,NULL,1900,'H','su2, su3','Follow-up option from the OD Moon Glider sway that''s hit confirmable (18F window); Puts the opponent into a limited juggle state on hit (can only really extend the combo by canceling into SA2 / SA3 / CA; +42 KD when hitting grounded opponents which sets up for a safe jump if close enough to the corner',70,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('d1b9e95f-ac17-4ba4-a6d2-b56b5811406f','Elena','Meteor Volley','','236236K','super',9,5,24,-68,NULL,1800,'H','','Invincible to airborne strikes on frames 1-23; Has no strike/throw/projectile invincibility (cannot be used as a reversal); Airborne on frames 9-65 (Forced Knockdown state); Armor Break; Depletes 0.5 Drive Bar on hit for the opponent; Incurs 30% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo; Incurs 10% immediate scaling and counts as 2 hits of damage scaling when comboed into; Cannot hit cross-up (behind Elena); Launches the opponent into a limited juggle state (follow-up juggles always possible)',71,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('844325a2-fd76-415c-b7f7-5172414bb313','Elena','Revival Dance','','236236P','super',12,6,62,-47,NULL,2800,'H','','Fully invincible on frames 1-17; Armor Break; Depletes 1 Drive Bar on hit for the opponent; Excellent anti-fireball tool due to its invincibility and forward movement; Slow startup makes it a risky reversal option (can be safely meatied by light normals); On HIT only; Can hold down during the move to sacrifice damage (1950 damage instead of 2800) and oki (+1 HKD instead of +25 HKD) to instead heal yourself by 1300 HP (13% health); This healing is unaffected by scaling and deals the same Drive damage to the opponent as the regular version',72,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('132e4495-16ac-444e-bfdb-d902f04c10f6','Elena','Song of the Grasslands','','214214K','super',8,4,68,-54,NULL,4000,'H','','Fully invincible on frames 1-11; Armor Break; Depletes 1.5 Drive Bars on hit for the opponent; Super cinematic time regenerates ~2.1 Drive Bars for Elena; Incurs 10% damage scaling when canceled into from Specials; Great anti-air at mid to long range, but can whiff under closer range jumps and cannot hit cross-up (behind Elena)',73,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('06a2f1dd-35c5-4612-a614-1a0e918258cb','Elena','Song of the Grasslands (Critical Art)','','214214K (CA)','super',8,4,68,-54,NULL,4500,'H','','Fully invincible on frames 1-11; Armor Break; Depletes 2 Drive Bars on hit for the opponent; Super cinematic time regenerates ~2.1 Drive Bars for Elena; Incurs 10% damage scaling when canceled into from Specials; Great anti-air at mid to long range, but can whiff under closer range jumps and cannot hit cross-up (behind Elena)',74,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('1a0a7a0f-7f34-4500-94d9-64ae1f22da98','Guile','Stand LP','','5LP','normal',5,3,7,-2,4,300,'H','ch, sp, su','Chains into stand LP / crouch LP / crouch LK; Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo',1,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('0877b343-ce55-4778-888f-e5c492cd163d','Guile','Stand MP','','5MP','normal',7,3,15,0,6,600,'H','sp, su, tc','Main combo starter; Has a b+HP Target Combo follow-up',2,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('94b61924-bd67-4117-91e4-81dff161fe76','Guile','Stand HP','','5HP','normal',7,3,23,-6,-1,900,'H','sp, su','Fully cancelable combo / whiff punish tool; Decent whiff punish tool with its Punish Counter stagger effect (+14 on Punish Counter); Situational anti-air on the later 2 active frames; There is a brief extended hurtbox on frame 6 of start-up (1F before active) that is strike invincible (cannot counter-poke projectiles); Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo',3,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
