('393e4f67-6ea3-4d11-aaa1-8abb377e5f4d','Guile','Crouch LP','','2LP','normal',4,3,8,-2,5,300,'H','ch, sp, su','Chains into stand LP / crouch LP / crouch LK; Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo; Topmost hurtboxes on frames 1-6 are vulnerable only to airborne attacks (this is to discourage its use as an anti-air)',7,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('814ccad9-32ae-4769-b3a3-2ee83285829e','Guile','Crouch MP','','2MP','normal',6,3,13,-2,4,600,'H','sp, su, tc','Has very low pushback on hit; Cancelable into itself (d+MP Target Combo); +3F extra recovery frames (16F) on whiff; Topmost hurtboxes on frames 1-8 are vulnerable only to airborne attacks (this is to discourage its use as an anti-air)',8,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
