('9f9491ec-a8b2-4cef-87f2-35b595d0cb76','Guile','Spinning Back Knuckle','','6HP','normal',16,3,20,3,5,800,'H','','Cannot hit crouch; Moves Guile forward with strong + frames on block; Has some juggle potential',20,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
