('b76e763c-f90e-421a-b1c6-6f4082dc9ae1','Jamie','OD Arrow Kick','','623KK','special',6,9,51,-43,NULL,1350,'H','','Fully invincible on frames 1-9; Invincible to airborne strikes on frames 10-12; Low crushes on frames 10-21; Does the follow-up strike on HIT only; Jamie becomes fully invincible again for the follow-up strike on frames 15-38; Follow-up hit is airborne with 11F landing recovery; Cannot hit cross-up (behind Jamie); In specific juggle scenarios this move can be juggled into another OD Arrow Kick',65,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('81031390-04b0-49f4-b309-aa61ed078b6e','Jamie','Breakin''','','236236K','super',8,2,74,-60,NULL,1980,'H','','Strike and Throw invincible on frames 1-12; Armor Break; Depletes 0.5 Drive Bar on hit for the opponent; Can hold down during the move to get +1 Drink Level as well as restoring 1/2 extra bar of Drive Gauge | 1/12th (~8%) of Burnout Gauge, in exchange for sacrificing some damage (-315 damage) and some oki (+4 KDA instead of +12); Moves Jamie quite far forward during its initial active frames, with impressive reach on its hitboxes; Jamie''s fastest startup invincible Super Art makes this the ideal Reversal option while in Burnout; KDA is usually higher juggled into which can lead into stronger oki (Example: +3 extra KDA when juggled into after OD Palm)',66,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('d6372826-3f49-4783-bb48-fde9a3eaf527','Jamie','The Devil''s Song','','214214P','super',1,NULL,5,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','Duration of 900 frames (15 seconds) - The remaining timer freezes during any hitstop; Temporarily grants Jamie access to Drink Level 4 as well as restoring 1 bar of Drive Gauge | 1/6th (~17%) of Burnout Gauge; Jamie still only deals 105% damage during this super if it''s activated during Drink Levels 0-3 as opposed to the 110% damage Jamie normally deals at Drink Level 4; Jamie does not build any Super meter while this super buff is active (however if he''s already at Drink Level 4 when he activates this Super, then there''s no buff timer so he can continue building Super meter); When used already at Drink Level 4: Instantly restores 3 bars of Jamie''s Drive Gauge | 1/2 (50%) of Burnout Gauge; Jamie retains all the Drink Levels he previously had after the Super''s duration expires',67,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('41643524-613b-4806-8d78-644d87acf72c','Jamie','Getsuga Saiho','','236236P','super',10,3,42,-27,NULL,2340,'H','','Fully invincible on frames 1-12; Launches the opponent into a free juggle state on the regular version; Only goes into cinematic on first hit (only get a regular +14 knockdown for 450 damage on second hit); Armor Break; Depletes 1.5 Drive Bars on hit for the opponent; Super cinematic time regenerates ~1.8 Drive Bars for Jamie; Incurs 10% damage scaling when canceled into from specials; Puts the opponent into a free juggle state (and resets the current Juggle Counter to 0) allowing for free-form follow-up juggles',68,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('96984d09-5c4a-4ce3-b07b-b3d0075f1d27','Jamie','Getsuga Saiho (Critical Art)','','236236P (CA)','super',10,3,42,-27,NULL,4050,'H','','Fully invincible on frames 1-12; Only goes into cinematic on first hit (only get a regular +14 knockdown for 450 damage on second hit); Armor Break; Depletes 2 Drive Bars on hit for the opponent; Super cinematic time regenerates ~2.2 Drive Bars for Jamie; Incurs 10% damage scaling when canceled into from specials',69,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('09088524-6ef2-4b71-9c84-9f1cfb6b14dc','Jamie','Stand LP [D1]','','5LP','normal',5,3,9,-3,2,285,'H','sp, su, tc','Very good range for a light normal (slightly shorter range hitbox for crouching opponents); Cancelable into the LP > LK > MP target combo (works even from max range stand LP); Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo',70,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('eb75bf5e-b7e6-46c1-b12b-23d533fc7472','Jamie','Stand MP [D1]','','5MP','normal',8,4,14,2,6,570,'H','','Jamie''s main frametrap / combo tool',71,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('91af6905-7925-46e8-8995-3c1cc1fe710f','Jamie','Stand HP [D1]','','5HP','normal',5,1,20,-3,1,855,'H','sp, su','Very fast start-up and fast 3-hit string makes this a super strong tool against Drive Impacts; Last hit has pretty good range and makes for a good whiff punish tool (the third hit is effectively 12F start-up) with +5 on Punish allowing for a follow-up combo (can be spaced so that the third strike hits meaty up to +7 on Punish Counter); Only cancelable on the first 2 hits; Leaves Jamie up close for pressure / mixup on hit / counter-hit; Carries over Counter-Hit / Punish Counter bonus frame advantage to all hits; Has naturally high juggle potential (without Drive Rush) and maintains juggle state on last 2 hits (various juggle opportunities with this move); Juggle Limit / Increase / Start: 0*1*2 / 1*1*1 / 1*1*1; Hatson''s favorite move in SF6 so far',72,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('d4f6df23-dfac-4f66-ba35-aad60794f03b','Jamie','Stand LK [D1]','','5LK','normal',5,2,11,-1,3,285,'H','ch, sp, su','Chains into crouch LP / crouch LK / stand LK; Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo; Can infinitely chain into itself; Moves Jamie''s positioning forward a little bit so chaining from this LK into other lights grants them extra range; Has a different animation when chained into from his other light normals',73,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('2455ac38-027f-4218-8f9f-1e75142f3598','Jamie','Stand MK [D1]','','5MK','normal',9,3,17,-3,2,570,'H','sp, su','Great poke and buffer tool at close / mid-range; Jamie lifts up his front leg hurtbox on frames 4-12 making this a good tool against low attacks; +1F extra recovery frames (18F) on whiff; Jamie''s only cancelable medium that combos into HP Palm on Punish Counter (very useful in mid-range footsies prior to reaching Drink Level 2)',74,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('b2d3efdf-897d-4f05-aa1e-f07d1dd2706f','Jamie','Stand HK [D1]','','5HK','normal',15,3,21,-5,3,760,'H','sp, su','Causes a crumple-like free juggle state on a grounded Punish Counter (opponent is in a grounded state for +9 frames before going airborne); Puts airborne opponents into a limited juggle state; Huge range for a special cancelable normal; If canceled into Drink off a Punish Counter in the corner, Jamie can do a juggle follow-up with a 4F (crouch LP) before the opponent falls onto the ground (can juggle into 5F stand LK if the drink activates the Drink Level 4 install); The brief extended leg hurtbox on frame 14 of start-up (1F before active) is strike invincible (cannot counter-poke projectiles); Juggle Limit / Increase / Start: 0 / 0 / 1',75,datetime('now'),datetime('now'));
INSERT INTO frame_data (id,character,move_name,move_name_jp,input,category,startup,active,recovery,on_block,on_hit,damage,guard,cancel_into,notes,sort_order,updated_at,created_at) VALUES
('0ae42b5f-c8d8-4a1f-b9a0-51264c464c5c','Jamie','Crouch LP [D1]','','2LP','normal',4,2,9,-1,5,237,'H','ch, sp, su','Chains into crouch LP / crouch LK / stand LK; Jamie''s only 4F normal; Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo; Deals 50 less base damage (250 at Drink Level 2) than all other crouch jabs in the game (normally deal 300 damage)',76,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('e67ac5e1-f028-4716-8d77-bd97d24986a6','Jamie','Crouch MP [D1]','','2MP','normal',6,3,13,-1,5,570,'H','sp, su','Good combo / buffer / frametrap tool with strong hitbox priority; +2F extra recovery frames (15F) on whiff',77,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('6de0a14f-0deb-4bdc-a2c3-0d93f8d22d9d','Jamie','Crouch HP [D1]','','2HP','normal',8,5,23,-8,0,855,'H','sp, su','Forces stand; Jamie''s head hurtbox is invincible to airborne strikes on frames 8-32; Primary combo tool as well as a strong anti-air (but cannot hit cross-up behind Jamie); Only cancelable on the first two active frames',78,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('098255ef-1f88-41db-a2dd-39ee6e1d22c1','Jamie','Crouch LK [D1]','','2LK','normal',5,2,11,-3,1,190,'L','ch','Chains into crouch LP / crouch LK / stand LK; Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo',79,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('01e3aa0a-5e0b-4cee-a79c-d1894b2d691b','Jamie','Crouch MK [D1]','','2MK','normal',7,3,18,-6,-1,475,'L','sp, su','Incurs 20% hit damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo; Has big pushback on block making this move relatively safe to poke with and to bait retaliations from the opponent',80,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('93e854d6-5113-46d8-8fa5-324bee16cc53','Jamie','Crouch HK [D1]','','2HK','normal',9,2,28,-11,NULL,720,'L','','Second hit has quite bit a further range than the first hit; Has a Target Combo follow-up (can hit confirm into this) that''s a great way of raising drink level while still maintaining oki mixups in the corner; Can be spaced out to make only the second hit connect, making the move deceptively safe on block; Second hit is not a low after the first hit is blocked; Has high natural juggle limit; Juggle Limit / Increase / Start: 5*5 / 1*1 / 1*1',81,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('a009a9cc-10f9-4f33-b859-61b21201557c','Jamie','Jump LP [D1]','','8LP','normal',5,9,NULL,NULL,NULL,285,'M','','Cross-up; Can be used as an instant Overhead',82,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('b73c1b67-7c43-445c-b46e-45324a5627e4','Jamie','Jump MP [D1]','','8MP','normal',7,4,NULL,NULL,NULL,665,'M','sp','Puts airborne opponents into a juggle state; Cancelable into his Divekick (Drink Level 1) during forward jump; Shifts the normal jumping hurtbox upward during start-up (helps with avoiding some attacks); Juggle Limit / Increase / Start: 2 / 1 / 1',83,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('dc4396b6-0e32-48ce-bff2-10932023758b','Jamie','Jump HP [D1]','','8HP','normal',10,6,NULL,NULL,NULL,760,'M','','Spikes down airborne opponents; Has some natural juggle limit (similar to jump MP); I whip my hair back and forth!',84,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('707d99ba-58c5-4540-bcd3-527c8794c56d','Jamie','Jump LK [D1]','','8LK','normal',6,6,NULL,NULL,NULL,285,'M','','Has the furthest horizontal range of all of Jamie''s jump-ins',85,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('787d4a8d-6193-44f7-bc33-eb8b376b868d','Jamie','Jump MK [D1]','','8MK','normal',7,6,NULL,NULL,NULL,475,'M','','Cross-up',86,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('8dc93d73-6117-4f80-8368-b78efb7b7d88','Jamie','Jump HK [D1]','','8HK','normal',8,3,NULL,NULL,NULL,810,'M','','Amazing air-to-air / anti-air tool due to the rewards it leads to on airborne hit; Both hits put airborne opponents into a limited juggle state; Shifts the normal jumping hurtbox upward during start-up (helps with avoiding some attacks); Juggle Limit / Increase / Start: 0*1 / 1*0 / 1*1',87,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('0a0ad941-6ac8-4c1b-a6f2-8726bdc9d084','Jamie','Indian Step [D1]','','5LK (mash)','normal',5,2,11,-1,3,285,'H','sp, su','Chains into crouch LP / crouch LK / stand LK; Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo; Can infinitely chain into itself; Moves Jamie''s positioning forward a little bit so chaining from this LK into other lights grants them extra range; We do a little trolling',88,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('ee978dbe-5be7-4f14-8ed7-5d8367241c68','Jamie','Tensei Kick [D1]','','2KK','normal',9,3,22,-8,NULL,570,'H','j','Jamie''s head and kicking leg hurtboxes are invincible to airborne strikes on frames 9-11 (during the 3 active frames); Jump cancelable on HIT only (Jamie always jumps forward no matter which up direction is pressed); Launches opponent into a limited juggle state (free juggle state if used from Drive Rush); Primary combo / juggle tool as well as a good anti-air (but cannot hit cross-up behind Jamie); Counts as 2 hits of damage scaling when used as the start of a combo (like when anti-airing); Juggle Limit / Increase / Start: 0 / 1 / 1',89,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('00c97c9e-308b-433c-bb1b-68ed8193df07','Jamie','Falling Star Kick [D1]','','6MK','normal',22,3,20,-3,1,570,'M','','Overhead; High profile (crushes lows) on frames 10-19; No target combo follow-up unless at Drink Level 2; Gains twice as much range at Drink Level 2 and higher; Can be spaced to hit on later active frames; Spiked knockdown on airborne opponents (no follow-up juggle possible); Juggle Limit / Increase / Start: 0 / 1 / 1',90,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('b97bd071-5951-4ace-b7b8-6a0040e1eac1','Jamie','Hermit''s Elbow [D1]','','4HP','normal',18,4,20,-3,1,760,'H','su','Jamie pulls back his hurtboxes on frames 5-12 before striking back with his elbow (can be used to avoid throws and attacks, and then Punish Countering them); Doesn''t pull back the hurtboxes as far or have as much range as the Drink Level 3 version (but has better combo potential); No target combo follow-up unless at Drink Level 3; Cancelable into all Supers on Hit / Block; Juggle Limit / Increase / Start: 0 / 1 / 1',91,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('4395933f-76df-45b3-97b0-6321bd1cafff','Jamie','Senei Kick [D1]','','6HK','normal',16,3,20,-3,3,855,'H','su','Not a low attack (despite what it looks like); Very good range (reaches about 60% screen length); No target combo follow-up unless at Drink Level 4; Cancelable into all Supers on Hit / Block; Juggle Limit / Increase / Start: 0 / 1 / 1',92,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('19a5ed7a-fb7e-43ce-ae2a-fe298895fb57','Jamie','Phantom Sway [D1]','','2HK > HK','normal',12,3,43,-28,NULL,475,'L*H','','Jamie''s optimal juggle ender to raising his drink levels; Has a high Juggle Limit; Juggle Limit / Increase / Start: 5*5*8 / 1*1*1 / 1*1*1',93,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('58a281b9-ff33-44e4-8e6f-49df8e9690d7','Jamie','Phantom Sway + Drink [D1]','','2HK > HK > P','normal',9,2,61,-46,NULL,475,'L*H','','Grants +1 Drink Level to Jamie; Restores 1/4 extra bar of Drive Gauge | 1/24th (~4%) of Burnout Gauge; Good way to restore some Drive Gauge / Burnout while still maintaining a strike / throw mixup in the corner; Juggle Limit / Increase / Start: 5*5*8 / 1*1*1 / 1*1*1',94,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('e1ea4743-c5d1-46d5-be71-6f2c3c57312a','Jamie','Bitter Strikes 1 (Drink 1)','','5LP > 5LK','normal',6,2,16,-8,-3,190,'H','tc','Good checking tool in neutral against incoming moves like Drive Rush; The follow-up MP is hit confirmable on hit/block',95,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('6ffe0c7d-5d03-438d-b069-87e7a57f8403','Jamie','Bitter Strikes 2 (Drink 1)','','5LP > 5LK > 5MP','normal',8,3,23,-10,-1,475,'H','sp, su','Primary combo tool; Fully cancelable unlike the second hit; All hits combo even from max range stand LP',96,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('3c18fab8-9938-4b38-b4d7-9f2996760101','Jamie','Back Shaver [D1]','','LPLK','throw',5,3,23,NULL,NULL,1139,'T','','Throw Loop: Dash up for +4 mixup between throw/strike (not possible on mid-screen back-roll); Can press / hold the LK button during the throw to restore 1/2 extra bar of Drive Gauge | 1/12th (~8%) of Burnout Gauge while sacrificing some oki (+7 KD instead of +23); Gets +70% damage increase (1937 damage), HKD (denies back-roll option on wake-up), and depletes 1 bar of Drive Gauge on a Punish Counter',97,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('35c68e04-e136-41a5-8416-683041b9bb6a','Jamie','Wheel Punch [D1]','','4LPLK','throw',5,3,23,NULL,NULL,1139,'T','','Back Throw Loop: Can Drive Rush into meaty strike / throw mix when performed while cornered; Can also do meaty MP / OD Palm for + frames as well as both giving follow-up combos on hit; Gets +70% damage increase (1836 damage), HKD (denies back-roll option on wake-up), and depletes 1 bar of Drive Gauge on a Punish Counter',98,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('b38befa1-c1be-4827-8a4c-52d8722afa08','Jamie','Drive Impact: Vainglory Strike [D1]','','HPHK','unique',26,2,35,-3,NULL,760,'H','','2 hits of armor on frames 1-27; Damages opponents Drive Gauge on Block (1/2 bar) | Hit (1 bar) | Counter-Hit (1.25 bar) | Punish Counter (1.5 bar); Knocks down on hit; Crumples on Punish Counter or after absorbing at least 1 attack during start-up (+21 frames before the crumple state goes airborne, followed by airborne state on frames 22-46 before they are grounded) which counts as 2 hits of damage scaling; If the armor absorbs an attack it slows the overall start-up by 1F (27F total instead of 26F); Pushes the opponent far back on hit or block and causes a wall splat if they hit the wall; Wall Splat on block adds 20% damage penalty on the next hit; Wall splats on hit or during Burnout counts as 2 hits of damage scaling; Wall Splat puts opponent into a special juggle state where the next move juggles them even if it doesn''t normally (similar juggle rules as from Drive Rush); Does not cause wall splat if combo''d into from other moves or unblockable setups (Lock); Puts airborne opponents into a long spinning free juggle state when hit as a Punish Counter; Regular KDA without a Wall Splat: +35 KD; Corner wall splat on HIT: +65 KD | Block: +72 HKD; KDA can vary greatly depending on how high the opponent wall splats (higher KDA the higher they wall splat); Can clash with other Drive Impacts if they collide on the same active frame (start at exactly the same time); Costs 1 bar of Drive Gauge; The scrub killer',99,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('19410dc1-c58a-44b2-8571-b681b488c5b4','Jamie','Drive Reversal: Leg Sweep [D1]','','6HPHK','unique',20,3,26,-6,NULL,475,'H','','Fully invincible on frames 1-22 (frames 1-20 when used on wake-up as a Reversal); Armor Break (blows through all armor like Drive Impact); Can be performed during blockstun or from a successful parry (trying to Drive Reversal after the blockstun is over will result in a Drive Impact); Can also be performed during wake-up as a Reversal, doing it this way speeds up the start-up frames by 2 frames (18F start-up instead of 20F); Drive Reversal immediately removes the current blockstun you''re in and starts the attack; Causes a 4F screen freeze that occurs after the 6th start-up frame, which can mess up the opponents input timing, or enable them to do a simple input OS to counter the Drive Reversal; Safe on block (-2) when used against an opponent currently in Burnout; Costs 2 bars of Drive Gauge',100,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('df50d2c6-a760-4f01-a94e-2ea09f7747b0','Jamie','LP Freeflow Strikes [D1]','','236LP','special',13,2,24,-6,-1,332,'H','su3','Cancelable into follow-up Punch / Kick rekkas (Punch rekkas can even be performed on whiff); Canceling into further Rekka punches is delayed a few frames on whiff compared to on hit / block; Cancelable into level 3 Super on Hit / Block',101,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('af73e24e-5d6f-4538-ae2c-cc7e708a782c','Jamie','LP Freeflow Strikes 2 [D1]','','236LP > 6P','special',13,2,28,-13,-3,332,'H','','Can be performed on whiff (but is delayed a few frames compared to when performed on hit / block); Normally a true blockstring but can have up to a 2F gap on block if this follow-up Rekka input is delayed',102,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
