('ae6428e4-b638-4eae-a2b9-a4277f3dfe39','Jamie','LP Freeflow Kicks 2 [D1]','','236LP > 6K','special',14,2,32,-15,-7,237,'H','','First kick follow-up is only possible on Hit / Block (not on whiff like the punch follow-ups); Normally a true blockstring but can have up to a 3F gap on block if this follow-up Rekka input is delayed',104,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
