('dc3beef5-2ce7-4b3b-a69b-0c59acffbb70','Jamie','MK Arrow Kick [D1]','','623MK','special',8,9,51,-43,NULL,1140,'H','','Invincible to airborne strikes on frames 1-14; Low crushes on frames 8-23; Does the follow-up strike on HIT only; Jamie becomes fully invincible for the follow-up strike on frames 17-40; Follow-up hit is airborne with 18F landing recovery; Cannot hit cross-up (behind Jamie)',126,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('221321d1-9186-4714-aedd-31a0ef76220d','Jamie','HK Arrow Kick [D1]','','623HK','special',10,9,51,-43,NULL,1330,'H','','Invincible to airborne strikes on frames 1-16; Low crushes on frames 10-25; Does the follow-up strike on HIT only; Jamie becomes fully invincible for the follow-up strike on frames 19-42; Follow-up hit is airborne with 8F landing recovery (HK version recovers the fastest which is important for some juggle scenarios); Cannot hit cross-up (behind Jamie); In specific juggle scenarios this move can be juggled into things like OD Arrow Kick or SA1 / SA3 (SA3 juggle is significantly rarer than the OD Arrow Kick or SA1 juggles)',127,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('d3ca9a72-89d0-41f2-b129-2bf17c72aa82','Jamie','OD Arrow Kick [D1]','','623KK','special',6,9,51,-43,NULL,1424,'H','','Fully invincible on frames 1-9; Invincible to airborne strikes on frames 10-12; Low crushes on frames 10-21; Does the follow-up strike on HIT only; Jamie becomes fully invincible again for the follow-up strike on frames 15-38; Follow-up hit is airborne with 11F landing recovery; Cannot hit cross-up (behind Jamie); In specific juggle scenarios this move can be juggled into another OD Arrow Kick',128,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('761ab8ab-dadc-48a5-9c87-74467780d7ed','Jamie','Luminous Dive Kick (Drink 1)','','214K (air)','special',11,1,13,-8,NULL,950,'H','','Not an Overhead; Only possible during a forward jump; Divekick trajectory is determined by button strength; LK (Classic) / L (Modern): Short | MK (Classic) / M (Modern): Mid | HK (Classic) / H (Modern): Far; Can Tiger Knee motion this (214~9) to do it closer to the ground; Forced Knockdown state while airborne; Jamie can juggle afterwards on a grounded opponent if the Divekick connects low to the ground; Spiked knockdown on airborne opponents (no juggle possible after); Good tool to bait throw techs or as an escape from corner throw loops; Frame advantage and KDA improves the lower Jamie connects to the opponents body; Jamie has no head hurtbox during the entire landing recovery frames, and transitions into a crouch state on the last recovery frame',129,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('5973ca78-1713-47af-a309-5131c765c60e','Jamie','OD Luminous Dive Kick (Drink 1)','','214KK (air)','special',11,1,13,-4,NULL,760,'H','','Puts opponent into a limited OTG juggle state; Not an Overhead; Only possible during a forward jump; Can Tiger Knee motion this (214~9) to do it closer to the ground; Forced Knockdown state while airborne; Good tool to bait throw techs or as an escape from corner throw loops; Frame advantage and KDA improves the lower Jamie connects to the opponents body; Incurs a 10% damage scaling penalty; Jamie has no head hurtbox during the entire landing recovery frames, and transitions into a crouch state on the last recovery frame',130,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('82c42d26-0549-4148-b6fe-672d62d08bd6','Jamie','Breakin'' [D1]','','236236K','super',8,2,74,-60,NULL,2084,'H','','Strike and Throw invincible on frames 1-12; Armor Break; Depletes 0.5 Drive Bar on hit for the opponent; Can hold down during the move to get +1 Drink Level as well as restoring 1/2 extra bar of Drive Gauge | 1/12th (~8%) of Burnout Gauge, in exchange for sacrificing some damage (-331 damage) and some oki (+4 KDA instead of +12); Moves Jamie quite far forward during its initial active frames, with impressive reach on its hitboxes; Jamie''s fastest startup invincible Super Art makes this the ideal Reversal option while in Burnout; KDA is usually higher juggled into which can lead into stronger oki (Example: +3 extra KDA when juggled into after OD Palm); Juggle Limit: 20',131,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('bb023c66-553b-497e-8394-2a3c44a568fb','Jamie','Getsuga Saiho [D1]','','236236P','super',10,3,42,-27,NULL,2469,'H','','Fully invincible on frames 1-12; Launches the opponent into a free juggle state on the regular version; Only goes into cinematic on first hit (only get a regular +14 knockdown for 475 damage on second hit); Armor Break; Depletes 1.5 Drive Bars on hit for the opponent; Super cinematic time regenerates ~1.8 Drive Bars for Jamie; Incurs 10% damage scaling when canceled into from specials; Puts the opponent into a free juggle state (and resets the current Juggle Counter to 0) allowing for free-form follow-up juggles',132,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('221dea44-38e5-48d2-a81e-0e3e4424cc9c','Jamie','Getsuga Saiho (Critical Art) [D1]','','236236P','super',10,3,42,-27,NULL,4274,'H','','Fully invincible on frames 1-12; Only goes into cinematic on first hit (only get a regular +14 knockdown for 475 damage on second hit); Armor Break; Depletes 2 Drive Bars on hit for the opponent; Super cinematic time regenerates ~2.2 Drive Bars for Jamie; Incurs 10% damage scaling when canceled into from specials',133,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('27575a75-86cb-44a6-b09b-7af88a9917d5','Jamie','Stand LP [D2]','','5LP','normal',5,3,9,-3,2,300,'H','sp, su, tc','Very good range for a light normal (slightly shorter range hitbox for crouching opponents); Cancelable into the LP > LK > MP target combo (works even from max range stand LP); Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo',134,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('66aff32b-01f5-4b4b-9a83-d74c0f69be24','Jamie','Stand MP [D2]','','5MP','normal',8,4,14,2,6,600,'H','','Jamie''s main frametrap / combo tool',135,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('19b17404-5284-4328-8e3d-c0675094cf85','Jamie','Stand HP [D2]','','5HP','normal',5,1,20,-3,1,900,'H','sp, su','Great combo / juggle / punish / Drive Rush tool; Very fast start-up and fast 3-hit string makes this a super strong tool against Drive Impacts; Last hit has pretty good range and makes for a good whiff punish tool (the third hit is effectively 12F start-up) with +5 on Punish allowing for a follow-up combo (can be spaced so that the third strike hits meaty up to +7 on Punish Counter); Only cancelable on the first 2 hits; Leaves Jamie up close for pressure / mixup on hit / counter-hit; Carries over Counter-Hit / Punish Counter bonus frame advantage to all hits; Has naturally high juggle potential (without Drive Rush) and maintains juggle state on last 2 hits (various juggle opportunities with this move); Juggle Limit / Increase / Start: 0*1*2 / 1*1*1 / 1*1*1; Hatson''s favorite move in SF6 so far',136,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('1137f233-954d-4763-801a-162b403e18fd','Jamie','Stand LK [D2]','','5LK','normal',5,2,11,-1,3,300,'H','ch, sp, su','Chains into crouch LP / crouch LK / stand LK; Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo; Can infinitely chain into itself; Moves Jamie''s positioning forward a little bit so chaining from this LK into other lights grants them extra range; Has a different animation when chained into from his other light normals',137,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('a36aeded-8c1f-4a7e-8f7c-39480cb5c9c2','Jamie','Stand MK [D2]','','5MK','normal',9,3,17,-3,2,600,'H','sp, su','Great poke and buffer tool at close / mid-range; Jamie lifts up his front leg hurtbox on frames 4-12 making this a good tool against low attacks; +1F extra recovery frames (18F) on whiff; Jamie''s only cancelable medium that combos into HP Palm on Punish Counter (very useful in mid-range footsies prior to reaching Drink Level 2)',138,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('312b391a-efa3-41d1-a566-7eedbd731e07','Jamie','Stand HK [D2]','','5HK','normal',15,3,21,-5,3,800,'H','sp, su','Causes a crumple-like free juggle state on a grounded Punish Counter (opponent is in a grounded state for +9 frames before going airborne); Puts airborne opponents into a limited juggle state; Huge range for a special cancelable normal; If canceled into Drink off a Punish Counter in the corner, Jamie can do a juggle follow-up with a 4F (crouch LP) before the opponent falls onto the ground (can juggle into 5F stand LK if the drink activates the Drink Level 4 install); The brief extended leg hurtbox on frame 14 of start-up (1F before active) is strike invincible (cannot counter-poke projectiles); Juggle Limit / Increase / Start: 0 / 0 / 1',139,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('d13adbf5-26b4-409a-8991-8147aa620adc','Jamie','Crouch LP [D2]','','2LP','normal',4,2,9,-1,5,250,'H','ch, sp, su','Chains into crouch LP / crouch LK / stand LK; Jamie''s only 4F normal; Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo; Deals 50 less base damage (250 at Drink Level 2) than all other crouch jabs in the game (normally deal 300 damage)',140,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('061ffdcc-d532-44eb-847f-6c0c147e78d3','Jamie','Crouch MP [D2]','','2MP','normal',6,3,13,-1,5,600,'H','sp, su','Good combo / buffer / frametrap tool with strong hitbox priority; +2F extra recovery frames (15F) on whiff',141,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('90764ba3-e9aa-44db-9ca3-73cdc159d467','Jamie','Crouch HP [D2]','','2HP','normal',8,5,23,-8,0,900,'H','sp, su','Forces stand; Jamie''s head hurtbox is invincible to airborne strikes on frames 8-32; Primary combo tool as well as a strong anti-air (but cannot hit cross-up behind Jamie); Only cancelable on the first two active frames',142,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('2fecc68e-0aa7-4b28-8b4f-412f94d62085','Jamie','Crouch LK [D2]','','2LK','normal',5,2,11,-3,1,200,'L','ch','Chains into crouch LP / crouch LK / stand LK; Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo',143,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('2c574ba9-afb8-45ee-9360-07ba17abdec6','Jamie','Crouch MK [D2]','','2MK','normal',7,3,18,-6,-1,500,'L','sp, su','Incurs 20% hit damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo; Has big pushback on block making this move relatively safe to poke with and to bait retaliations from the opponent',144,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('d758d2f5-7107-419c-aa88-49d215cea975','Jamie','Crouch HK [D2]','','2HK','normal',9,2,28,-11,NULL,800,'L','','Second hit has quite bit a further range than the first hit; Has a Target Combo follow-up (can hit confirm into this) that''s a great way of raising drink level while still maintaining oki mixups in the corner; Can be spaced out to make only the second hit connect, making the move deceptively safe on block; Second hit is not a low after the first hit is blocked; Has high natural juggle limit; Juggle Limit / Increase / Start: 5*5 / 1*1 / 1*1',145,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
