('2c2ec5dc-5456-4b95-a5de-03e6dbc1ce3f','Jamie','Jump HK [D2]','','8HK','normal',8,3,NULL,NULL,NULL,900,'M','','Amazing air-to-air / anti-air tool due to the rewards it leads to on airborne hit; Both hits put airborne opponents into a limited juggle state; Shifts the normal jumping hurtbox upward during start-up (helps with avoiding some attacks); Juggle Limit / Increase / Start: 0*1 / 1*0 / 1*1',151,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('85c1e406-c439-42e3-b43c-55f1f6627623','Jamie','Indian Step [D2]','','5LK (mash)','normal',5,2,11,-1,3,300,'H','sp, su','Chains into crouch LP / crouch LK / stand LK; Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo; Can infinitely chain into itself; Moves Jamie''s positioning forward a little bit so chaining from this LK into other lights grants them extra range; We do a little trolling',152,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('cb169923-7540-414c-81e9-67284863f679','Jamie','Tensei Kick [D2]','','2KK','normal',9,3,22,-8,NULL,600,'H','j','Jamie''s head and kicking leg hurtboxes are invincible to airborne strikes on frames 9-11 (during the 3 active frames); Jump cancelable on HIT only (Jamie always jumps forward no matter which up direction is pressed); Launches opponent into a limited juggle state (free juggle state if used from Drive Rush); Primary combo / juggle tool as well as a good anti-air (but cannot hit cross-up behind Jamie); Counts as 2 hits of damage scaling when used as the start of a combo (like when anti-airing); Juggle Limit / Increase / Start: 0 / 1 / 1',153,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('5134dfed-10b1-41c6-bce6-56da230fb499','Jamie','Falling Star Kick [D2]','','6MK','normal',22,3,20,-3,1,600,'M','','Overhead; High profile (crushes lows) on frames 10-19; No target combo follow-up unless at Drink Level 2; Gains twice as much range at Drink Level 2 and higher; Can be spaced to hit on later active frames; Spiked knockdown on airborne opponents (no follow-up juggle possible); 17F Target Combo hit confirm window makes this a hit confirmable low crushing Overhead that leads to a drink (nice!); Juggle Limit / Increase / Start: 0 / 1 / 1',154,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('ed2bf4f2-b64b-483b-8472-753cd2faba92','Jamie','Hermit''s Elbow [D2]','','4HP','normal',18,4,20,-3,1,800,'H','su','Jamie pulls back his hurtboxes on frames 5-12 before striking back with his elbow (can be used to avoid throws and attacks, and then Punish Countering them); Doesn''t pull back the hurtboxes as far or have as much range as the Drink Level 3 version (but has better combo potential); No target combo follow-up unless at Drink Level 3; Cancelable into all Supers on Hit / Block; Juggle Limit / Increase / Start: 0 / 1 / 1',155,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('bf6be1b0-9111-46d9-97ce-0831a1ec9982','Jamie','Senei Kick [D2]','','6HK','normal',16,3,20,-3,3,900,'H','su','Not a low attack (despite what it looks like); Very good range (reaches about 60% screen length); No target combo follow-up unless at Drink Level 4; Cancelable into all Supers on Hit / Block; Juggle Limit / Increase / Start: 0 / 1 / 1',156,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('4dd922a5-43a1-4bd2-af25-433203ab6c51','Jamie','Phantom Sway [D2]','','2HK > HK','normal',12,3,43,-28,NULL,500,'L*H','','Jamie''s optimal juggle ender to raising his drink levels; Has a high Juggle Limit; Juggle Limit / Increase / Start: 5*5*8 / 1*1*1 / 1*1*1',157,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('117c2a58-d1c7-4905-983f-5cdaf710e450','Jamie','Phantom Sway + Drink [D2]','','2HK > HK > P','normal',9,2,61,-46,NULL,500,'L*H','','Grants +1 Drink Level to Jamie; Restores 1/4 extra bar of Drive Gauge | 1/24th (~4%) of Burnout Gauge; Good way to restore some Drive Gauge / Burnout while still maintaining a strike / throw mixup in the corner; Juggle Limit / Increase / Start: 5*5*8 / 1*1*1 / 1*1*1',158,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
