('938b7998-7c42-418e-97cc-ba3e98658a67','Jamie','OD Freeflow Strikes [D2]','','236PP','special',13,2,24,-3,1,450,'H','su2, su3','Cancelable into follow-up Punch / Kick rekkas (Punch rekkas can even be performed on whiff); The follow-up punch rekkas do not count as separate hits in terms of damage scaling (all hits deal the same damage %); Canceling into further Rekka punches is delayed a few frames on whiff compared to on hit / block; Cancelable into level 2 and 3 Supers on Hit / Block; Incurs 25% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo and counts as 2 hits for damage scaling (when this or Freeflow Strikes 3 is canceled into Level 2 or Level 3 Super)',182,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
