('308bb6f5-8399-406f-997a-b99e5b70cb40','Jamie','Getsuga Saiho [D3]','','236236P','super',10,3,42,-27,NULL,2729,'H','','Fully invincible on frames 1-12; Launches the opponent into a free juggle state on the regular version; Only goes into cinematic on first hit (only get a regular +14 knockdown for 525 damage on second hit); Armor Break; Depletes 1.5 Drive Bars on hit for the opponent; Super cinematic time regenerates ~1.8 Drive Bars for Jamie; Incurs 10% damage scaling when canceled into from specials; Puts the opponent into a free juggle state (and resets the current Juggle Counter to 0) allowing for free-form follow-up juggles',276,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('43d19211-72b8-4ba4-b197-134d3522ecea','Jamie','Getsuga Saiho (Critical Art) [D3]','','236236P','super',10,3,42,-27,NULL,4724,'H','','Fully invincible on frames 1-12; Only goes into cinematic on first hit (only get a regular +14 knockdown for 525 damage on second hit); Armor Break; Depletes 2 Drive Bars on hit for the opponent; Super cinematic time regenerates ~2.2 Drive Bars for Jamie; Incurs 10% damage scaling when canceled into from specials',277,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('698b9192-5682-486a-b773-529c56652ee4','Jamie','Stand LP [D4]','','5LP','normal',5,3,9,-3,2,330,'H','sp, su, tc','Very good range for a light normal (slightly shorter range hitbox for crouching opponents); Cancelable into the LP > LK > MP target combo (works even from max range stand LP); Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo',278,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('690b65b4-c80b-4569-82f6-bcfa907b03da','Jamie','Stand MP [D4]','','5MP','normal',8,4,14,2,6,660,'H','','Jamie''s main frametrap / combo tool',279,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('d6ce639e-6d5d-4511-9b46-b329b8965731','Jamie','Stand HP [D4]','','5HP','normal',5,1,20,-3,1,990,'H','sp, su','Very fast start-up and fast 3-hit string makes this a super strong tool against Drive Impacts; Last hit has pretty good range and makes for a good whiff punish tool (the third hit is effectively 12F start-up) with +5 on Punish allowing for a follow-up combo (can be spaced so that the third strike hits meaty up to +7 on Punish Counter); Only cancelable on the first 2 hits; Leaves Jamie up close for pressure / mixup on hit / counter-hit; Carries over Counter-Hit / Punish Counter bonus frame advantage to all hits; Has naturally high juggle potential (without Drive Rush) and maintains juggle state on last 2 hits (various juggle opportunities with this move); Juggle Limit / Increase / Start: 0*1*2 / 1*1*1 / 1*1*1; Hatson''s favorite move in SF6 so far',280,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('70c2035b-656d-42e6-90d2-f6a2c6360387','Jamie','Stand LK [D4]','','5LK','normal',5,2,11,-1,3,330,'H','ch, sp, su','Chains into crouch LP / crouch LK / stand LK; Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo; Can infinitely chain into itself; Moves Jamie''s positioning forward a little bit so chaining from this LK into other lights grants them extra range; Has a different animation when chained into from his other light normals',281,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('8a92c3f2-84e1-4b58-a34c-45ca1e841e90','Jamie','Stand MK [D4]','','5MK','normal',9,3,17,-3,2,660,'H','sp, su','Great poke and buffer tool at close / mid-range; Jamie lifts up his front leg hurtbox on frames 4-12 making this a good tool against low attacks; +1F extra recovery frames (18F) on whiff; Jamie''s only cancelable medium that combos into HP Palm on Punish Counter (very useful in mid-range footsies prior to reaching Drink Level 2)',282,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('4e35dc97-ee20-464d-a04a-7702a79b6d19','Jamie','Stand HK [D4]','','5HK','normal',15,3,21,-5,3,880,'H','sp, su','Causes a crumple-like free juggle state on a grounded Punish Counter (opponent is in a grounded state for +9 frames before going airborne); Puts airborne opponents into a limited juggle state; Huge range for a special cancelable normal; If canceled into Drink off a Punish Counter in the corner, Jamie can do a juggle follow-up with a 4F (crouch LP) before the opponent falls onto the ground (can juggle into 5F stand LK if the drink activates the Drink Level 4 install); The brief extended leg hurtbox on frame 14 of start-up (1F before active) is strike invincible (cannot counter-poke projectiles); Juggle Limit / Increase / Start: 0 / 0 / 1',283,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('30ac37a9-6581-4320-baf3-8d6b618055b4','Jamie','Crouch LP [D4]','','2LP','normal',4,2,9,-1,5,275,'H','ch, sp, su','Chains into crouch LP / crouch LK / stand LK; Jamie''s only 4F normal; Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo; Deals 50 less base damage (250 at Drink Level 2) than all other crouch jabs in the game (normally deal 300 damage)',284,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('2a6a3fd8-775b-4293-b860-79e2fb9ddd1e','Jamie','Crouch MP [D4]','','2MP','normal',6,3,13,-1,5,660,'H','sp, su','Good combo / buffer / frametrap tool with strong hitbox priority; +2F extra recovery frames (15F) on whiff',285,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('f20540d9-c8ea-4cc3-9bd8-4b5f5b16ab5f','Jamie','Crouch HP [D4]','','2HP','normal',8,5,23,-8,0,990,'H','sp, su','Forces stand; Jamie''s head hurtbox is invincible to airborne strikes on frames 8-32; Primary combo tool as well as a strong anti-air (but cannot hit cross-up behind Jamie); Only cancelable on the first two active frames',286,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('65c5c659-6437-4a8e-9b95-c32cc09168c6','Jamie','Crouch LK [D4]','','2LK','normal',5,2,11,-3,1,220,'L','ch','Chains into crouch LP / crouch LK / stand LK; Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo',287,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('e5221e67-9bc5-4e15-b853-a21685ebf3fe','Jamie','Crouch MK [D4]','','2MK','normal',7,3,18,-6,-1,550,'L','sp, su','Incurs 20% hit damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo; Has big pushback on block making this move relatively safe to poke with and to bait retaliations from the opponent',288,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('a9ec710f-7eee-48a6-9ae6-9ca08577d34c','Jamie','Crouch HK [D4]','','2HK','normal',9,2,28,-11,NULL,880,'L','','Second hit has quite bit a further range than the first hit; Has a Target Combo follow-up (can hit confirm into this) that''s a great way of raising drink level while still maintaining oki mixups in the corner; Can be spaced out to make only the second hit connect, making the move deceptively safe on block; Second hit is not a low after the first hit is blocked; Has high natural juggle limit; Juggle Limit / Increase / Start: 5*5 / 1*1 / 1*1',289,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('0954ebf2-34d9-4ca2-b48e-31b6908d08d3','Jamie','Jump LP [D4]','','8LP','normal',5,9,NULL,NULL,NULL,330,'M','','Cross-up; Can be used as an instant Overhead',290,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('b4de10a2-a24d-430c-b5e4-bf4ccb46b871','Jamie','Jump MP [D4]','','8MP','normal',7,4,NULL,NULL,NULL,770,'M','sp','Puts airborne opponents into a juggle state; Cancelable into his Divekick (Drink Level 1) during forward jump; Shifts the normal jumping hurtbox upward during start-up (helps with avoiding some attacks); Juggle Limit / Increase / Start: 2 / 1 / 1',291,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('7299ba50-b9fb-4143-8227-10ac84e80700','Jamie','Jump HP [D4]','','8HP','normal',10,6,NULL,NULL,NULL,880,'M','','Spikes down airborne opponents; Has some natural juggle limit (similar to jump MP); I whip my hair back and forth!',292,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('3fc238f8-fe9c-4e96-8979-9d0140aa6361','Jamie','Jump LK [D4]','','8LK','normal',6,6,NULL,NULL,NULL,330,'M','','Has the furthest horizontal range of all of Jamie''s jump-ins',293,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('d2ba8109-2f12-49a4-96f4-d4697cd48f09','Jamie','Jump MK [D4]','','8MK','normal',7,6,NULL,NULL,NULL,550,'M','','Cross-up',294,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('8696a085-1551-476f-af20-767aeaa5b980','Jamie','Jump HK [D4]','','8HK','normal',8,3,NULL,NULL,NULL,990,'M','','Amazing air-to-air / anti-air tool due to the rewards it leads to on airborne hit; Both hits put airborne opponents into a limited juggle state; Shifts the normal jumping hurtbox upward during start-up (helps with avoiding some attacks); Juggle Limit / Increase / Start: 0*1 / 1*0 / 1*1',295,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('7324a667-5953-4ec6-acce-6b42271a381d','Jamie','Indian Step [D4]','','5LK (mash)','normal',5,2,11,-1,3,330,'H','sp, su','Chains into crouch LP / crouch LK / stand LK; Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo; Can infinitely chain into itself; Moves Jamie''s positioning forward a little bit so chaining from this LK into other lights grants them extra range; We do a little trolling',296,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('58026539-4ab0-401c-99e8-d5a2e482e42b','Jamie','Tensei Kick [D4]','','2KK','normal',9,3,22,-8,NULL,660,'H','j','Jamie''s head and kicking leg hurtboxes are invincible to airborne strikes on frames 9-11 (during the 3 active frames); Jump cancelable on HIT only (Jamie always jumps forward no matter which up direction is pressed); Launches opponent into a limited juggle state (free juggle state if used from Drive Rush); Primary combo / juggle tool as well as a good anti-air (but cannot hit cross-up behind Jamie); Counts as 2 hits of damage scaling when used as the start of a combo (like when anti-airing); Juggle Limit / Increase / Start: 0 / 1 / 1',297,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('b8b89dba-b2f2-487d-b48e-9cd31ca62029','Jamie','Falling Star Kick [D4]','','6MK','normal',22,3,20,-3,1,660,'M','','Overhead; High profile (crushes lows) on frames 10-19; No target combo follow-up unless at Drink Level 2; Gains twice as much range at Drink Level 2 and higher; Can be spaced to hit on later active frames; Spiked knockdown on airborne opponents (no follow-up juggle possible); 17F Target Combo hit confirm window makes this a hit confirmable low crushing Overhead that leads to a drink (nice!); Juggle Limit / Increase / Start: 0 / 1 / 1',298,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('b7c33ee5-148c-4c02-b6db-f4cf26dde89f','Jamie','Hermit''s Elbow [D4]','','4HP','normal',18,4,21,-3,1,880,'H','su, tc','Jamie pulls back his hurtboxes on frames 5-12 before striking back with his elbow (can be used to avoid throws and attacks, and then Punish Countering them); This Drink Level 3 version pulls the hurtboxes back further and has more range; Cancelable into all Supers on Hit / Block; 2F less recovery frames on HIT only; See notes on Target Combo version for more information; Juggle Limit / Increase / Start: 0 / 1 / 1',299,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('e0a13151-4b54-4cdb-8d64-243e2258616c','Jamie','Senei Kick [D4]','','6HK','normal',16,4,19,-3,3,990,'H','su, tc','Not a low attack (despite what it looks like); Very good range (seems slightly further than regular f+HK); Cancelable into all Supers on Hit / Block; See notes on Target Combo follow-ups for more information; Juggle Limit / Increase / Start: 0 / 1 / 1',300,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('22fe8749-a36c-4eff-b8d4-4ec2241f07e8','Jamie','Phantom Sway [D4]','','2HK > HK','normal',12,3,43,-28,NULL,550,'L*H','','Jamie''s optimal juggle ender to raising his drink levels; Has a high Juggle Limit; Juggle Limit / Increase / Start: 5*5*8 / 1*1*1 / 1*1*1',301,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('5f4b663f-c984-4917-b475-b376aa5fc009','Jamie','Phantom Sway + Drink [D4]','','2HK > HK > P','normal',9,2,61,-46,NULL,550,'L*H','','Restores 1 extra bar of Drive Gauge | 1/6th (~17%) of Burnout Gauge; Good way to restore some Drive Gauge / Burnout while still maintaining a strike / throw mixup in the corner; Usually +1 extra KDA when juggled into; Juggle Limit / Increase / Start: 5*5*8 / 1*1*1 / 0*1*1',302,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('6d5b455b-365e-42f2-bb3a-d94294550d5d','Jamie','Bitter Strikes 1 (Drink 1) [D4]','','5LP > 5LK','normal',6,2,16,-8,-3,220,'H','tc','Good checking tool in neutral against incoming moves like Drive Rush; The follow-up MP is hit confirmable on hit/block',303,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('0b446e8d-d713-4eaf-b5de-aa231fe0f9d3','Jamie','Bitter Strikes 2 (Drink 1) [D4]','','5LP > 5LK > 5MP','normal',8,3,23,-10,-1,550,'H','sp, su','Primary combo tool; Fully cancelable unlike the second hit; All hits combo even from max range stand LP',304,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('485239c8-7f06-46dc-ab5e-4d84eda5b04e','Jamie','Full Moon Kick (Drink 2) [D4]','','6MK > 5MK','normal',15,3,28,-14,NULL,1100,'M*H','','17F Target Combo hit confirm window makes this a hit confirmable low crushing Overhead that leads to a drink (nice!); First hit is an Overhead',305,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('e2fcc359-a882-4842-817d-3db53db24ef4','Jamie','Full Moon Kick + Drink (Drink 2) [D4]','','6MK > 5MK > P','normal',22,3,61,-43,NULL,1100,'M*H','','Restores 1 extra bar of Drive Gauge | 1/6th (~17%) of Burnout Gauge',306,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('831ee1fc-db0b-4a10-8bfc-63cba68cf063','Jamie','Intoxicated Assault 1 (Drink 3) [D4]','','4HP > 5HP','normal',21,4,20,-9,1,660,'H','su, tc','Cancelable into all Supers on Hit / Block; Jamie pulls back his hurtboxes before striking back with his elbow (can be used to avoid attacks and Punish Countering them); 2F gap between the 1st and 2nd hit hit on block (not a true blockstring unless it hits on active frames 3-4 of b+HP); Does not combo on hit unless it hits on active frames 2-4 of b+HP (elbow starter); Combos naturally on Counter-Hit and Punish Counter (this is hit confirmable)',307,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('02f83942-f1a7-4b37-9dec-30add5bd1bbb','Jamie','Intoxicated Assault 2 (Drink 3) [D4]','','4HP > 5HP > 5HK','normal',21,3,37,-20,NULL,880,'H','','Airborne on frames 18-27 (Forced Knockdown state) on the last HK hit; 6F gap between the 2nd and 3rd hit on block (can be interrupted by 6F normals which puts Jamie into a Forced Knockdown state for a follow-up juggle combo; A hit confirm style target combo that knocks down opponent on last hit; Does not combo on hit unless it hits on active frames 2-4 of b+HP (elbow starter); Combos naturally on Counter-Hit and Punish Counter (this is hit confirmable)',308,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('1d60ac2a-3525-4c64-9d72-bce4c31ad463','Jamie','Ransui Haze (Drink 4)','','6HK > 4HK','normal',16,4,76,NULL,NULL,990,'H','tc','Can be performed on whiff; Cancels into 3 different follow-ups depending on timing of the punch button between frames 25-100; Easily hit confirmable into Sway > Headbutt',309,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('c78a3410-60a6-4766-8ef6-81dd50bd3db3','Jamie','Ransui Haze Headbutt (Drink 4)','','6HK > 4HK > 5P (headbutt)','normal',15,4,28,-12,NULL,935,'H','sp, su','Can be performed on whiff and reaches quite far; Headbutt can be delayed a lot (23-43F after the Step Kick); Easily hit confirmable; Fully cancelable on Hit and Block; Combos normally on hit from Ransui Haze (f+HK > b+HK stance); Counts as 2 hits of damage scaling when used in the middle of a combo (like after the prior f+HK Step Kick hits)',310,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('c5978e93-c592-46cb-9504-5a0cc8059187','Jamie','Ransui Haze Triple Fist (Drink 4)','','6HK > 4HK > 5P (spinning fists)','normal',4,2,27,-9,NULL,1320,'H','sp, su','Can be performed on whiff; Spinning Fists can be delayed a lot (36-60F after the Step Kick); Fully cancelable on Hit and Block',311,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('ecf7b62e-67c1-4823-8478-1640167fb59a','Jamie','Ransui Haze Drink (Drink 4)','','6HK > 4HK > 5P (drink)','normal',76,NULL,52,NULL,NULL,880,'H','','Can be performed on whiff; Restores 1 extra bar of Drive Gauge | 1/6th (~17%) of Burnout Gauge; Rewards a second bar of Drive Gauge and another 1/6th (~17%) of Burnout Gauge if you don''t interrupt Jamie''s drinking (don''t input any direction or buttons)',312,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('4000aa76-0900-4d1e-945c-28b7e3a060d4','Jamie','Back Shaver [D4]','','LPLK','throw',5,3,23,NULL,NULL,1320,'T','','Throw Loop: Dash up for +4 mixup between throw/strike (not possible on mid-screen back-roll); Can press / hold the LK button during the throw to restore 1 extra bar of Drive Gauge | 1/6th (~17%) of Burnout Gauge while sacrificing some oki (+7 KD instead of +23); Gets +70% damage increase (2244 damage), HKD (denies back-roll option on wake-up), and depletes 1 bar of Drive Gauge on a Punish Counter',313,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('23f5931a-b565-44e2-977f-161a2a6ac471','Jamie','Wheel Punch [D4]','','4LPLK','throw',5,3,23,NULL,NULL,1320,'T','','Back Throw Loop: Can Drive Rush into meaty strike / throw mix when performed while cornered; Can also do meaty MP / OD Palm for + frames as well as both giving follow-up combos on hit; Gets +70% damage increase (1836 damage), HKD (denies back-roll option on wake-up), and depletes 1 bar of Drive Gauge on a Punish Counter',314,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('db8f2d80-fb5c-466c-b8ea-a62a6ffb3335','Jamie','Drive Impact: Vainglory Strike [D4]','','HPHK','unique',26,2,35,-3,NULL,880,'H','','2 hits of armor on frames 1-27; Damages opponents Drive Gauge on Block (1/2 bar) | Hit (1 bar) | Counter-Hit (1.25 bar) | Punish Counter (1.5 bar); Knocks down on hit; Crumples on Punish Counter or after absorbing at least 1 attack during start-up (+21 frames before the crumple state goes airborne, followed by airborne state on frames 22-46 before they are grounded) which counts as 2 hits of damage scaling; If the armor absorbs an attack it slows the overall start-up by 1F (27F total instead of 26F); Pushes the opponent far back on hit or block and causes a wall splat if they hit the wall; Wall Splat on block adds 20% damage penalty on the next hit; Wall splats on hit or during Burnout counts as 2 hits of damage scaling; Wall Splat puts opponent into a special juggle state where the next move juggles them even if it doesn''t normally (similar juggle rules as from Drive Rush); Does not cause wall splat if combo''d into from other moves or unblockable setups (Lock); Puts airborne opponents into a long spinning free juggle state when hit as a Punish Counter; Regular KDA without a Wall Splat: +35 KD; Corner wall splat on HIT: +65 KD | Block: +72 HKD; KDA can vary greatly depending on how high the opponent wall splats (higher KDA the higher they wall splat); Can clash with other Drive Impacts if they collide on the same active frame (start at exactly the same time); Costs 1 bar of Drive Gauge; The scrub killer',315,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('74b8f0bf-a8c9-4438-b434-b8daec27adbd','Jamie','Drive Reversal: Leg Sweep [D4]','','6HPHK','unique',20,3,26,-6,NULL,550,'H','','Fully invincible on frames 1-22 (frames 1-20 when used on wake-up as a Reversal); Armor Break (blows through all armor like Drive Impact); Can be performed during blockstun or from a successful parry (trying to Drive Reversal after the blockstun is over will result in a Drive Impact); Can also be performed during wake-up as a Reversal, doing it this way speeds up the start-up frames by 2 frames (18F start-up instead of 20F); Drive Reversal immediately removes the current blockstun you''re in and starts the attack; Causes a 4F screen freeze that occurs after the 6th start-up frame, which can mess up the opponents input timing, or enable them to do a simple input OS to counter the Drive Reversal; Safe on block (-2) when used against an opponent currently in Burnout; Costs 2 bars of Drive Gauge',316,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('e4178b4d-4e22-4bb4-91a2-337b846bfcf8','Jamie','LP Freeflow Strikes [D4]','','236LP','special',13,2,20,-3,1,440,'H','su3','Carries over Counter-Hit / Punish Counter bonus frame advantage to both hits; Cancelable into follow-up Punch / Kick rekkas (Punch rekkas can even be performed on whiff); Canceling into further Rekka punches is delayed a few frames on whiff compared to on hit / block; Cancelable into level 3 Super on Hit / Block',317,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
