('e0a11c75-7046-4c61-9952-89c9d582ea74','JP','Stand MP','','5MP','normal',12,3,21,-6,1,700,'H','','Solid poke tool with good range and hitbox priority',2,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('ceccd572-0d51-449c-a0ee-2d7798fb4836','JP','Stand HP','','5HP','normal',12,2,22,-3,3,800,'H','sp, su','JP''s main combo / juggle / punish tool, as well as being fully cancelable with solid range for checking the opponent; Very strong punish tool granting full combo conversions with Drive Rush; Puts airborne opponents into a limited juggle state; Has some juggle potential naturally without Drive Rush; Large but brief hurtbox extension 1F before active frames which is strike invincible (cannot counter-poke projectiles); Has slightly extended hurtboxes for the entire recovery frames; Counts as 2 hits of damage scaling when used as the start of a combo',3,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
