('32a98cc8-1dd4-4a8e-b3d4-8a44fb613b55','JP','Stand HK','','5HK','normal',12,4,17,2,7,800,'H','tc','Head hurtbox is invincible to airborne strikes on frames 9-15; Extended kicking leg is invincible to airborne strikes on frames 12-17; Jack-of-all-trades tool for JP that does a bit of everything (combo / pressure / oki / target-combo mixups / anti-air all in one button); Whiffs on crouching from further away',6,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('f23bec94-3dea-488d-a5b4-89ce1a73f611','JP','Crouch LP','','2LP','normal',4,2,11,-1,4,300,'H','ch, sp, su','JP''s only 4F normal option; Chains into stand LP / crouch LP / crouch LK; Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo; Topmost hurtboxes on frames 1-5 are vulnerable only to airborne attacks (this is to discourage its use as an anti-air)',7,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('ffc4630f-5d32-4b2b-8713-b35860f5099c','JP','Crouch MP','','2MP','normal',7,4,14,-2,6,600,'H','sp, su','Solid combo / poke / buffer tool; Topmost hurtboxes on frames 1-10 are vulnerable only to airborne attacks (this is to discourage its use as an anti-air)',8,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
