('0f42be9b-063d-4eaf-9fa5-ec498df61346','JP','Malice','','3HP','normal',16,3,31,-14,NULL,900,'L','','Very far range sweep (albeit a bit slow start-up) that can be very hard to punish on block for some characters when spaced out properly; JP ducks slightly during start-up losing his head hurtbox on frames 13-34 (but not low enough to get under Sagat''s MP/HP Tiger Shot) and is considered in a Standing state for the entire duration; Has naturally high juggle limit without Drive Rush',20,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('049b5bde-11f1-49f4-925b-505824927310','JP','Bylina','','6HK','normal',11,2,24,-5,NULL,900,'H','sp, su','Head and extended kicking leg hurtboxes are invincible to airborne strikes on frames 8-16; Solid horizontal anti-air (albeit a bit slow start-up) that launches opponents on hit into a limited juggle state; Core combo / juggle tool; Cannot hit cross-up (behind JP); First hit forces stand on hit; Second hit cannot hit crouching opponents, resulting in 3F worse frame advantage on block (-8); Both hits are cancelable (the cancel window executes after the second hits active frames)',21,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
