('158c1a77-b2df-4f33-bb10-438c0d261ff0','Juri','Crouch MP','','2MP','normal',6,4,14,-2,5,600,'H','sp, su','Great combo/buffer tool as well as an anti-air for horizontal approaches; +1 extra recovery frame (15F) on whiff only',8,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('04a0ca81-c3ba-410c-a620-cb10995908d1','Juri','Crouch HP','','2HP','normal',8,4,23,-11,3,900,'H','sp, su','Extended leg is invincible on airborne strikes on frames 8-15; Forces stand; Solid anti-air (Punish Counter launches airborne opponents into a free juggle state); Cannot hit cross-up (behind Juri); Launches opponent on hit into a juggle state (KD +34) when chained into and becomes jump cancelable on Hit while in Feng Shui Engine (Super Art Level 2); All of Juri''s air normals cause a juggle state after jump canceling from crouch HP during Feng Shui Engine (Super Art Level 2)',9,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
