('48f07c09-6544-4b14-a003-79901fbb25e3','Juri','Crouch MK','','2MK','normal',8,3,19,-6,1,500,'L','sp, su','Solid low poke / buffer tool with good range; Incurs a 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo',11,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
