('825445d8-d5e7-4fc2-8831-1646542b0174','Juri','> Shiren-sen','','214K > K (air)','special',6,4,12,NULL,NULL,1600,'H','','Puts the opponent into a limited juggle state; Juri is in a crouch state during the 12F landing recovery; Recovery frames listed does not include the airborne recovery frames which vary depending on height; KDA varies depending on how delayed the follow-up is input, as well as height (the higher Juri connects the higher the KDA is); Forced Knockdown state while airborne',53,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
