('a402496b-8978-496b-8ef3-04b0fe18b2f0','Juri','Jump LP [Super Install]','','j.LP','normal',5,6,NULL,NULL,NULL,100,'M','sp','Cancelable into Divekick during forward jump while in Feng Shui Engine (Super Art Level 2); Puts airborne opponents into a juggle state after jump canceling from crouch HP during Feng Shui Engine (Super Art level 2); Framedata / damage / properties listed here only refers to when chaining into this move via Feng Shui Engine (Super Art Level 2) - Refer to the regular Juri framedata sheet for the framedata / damage / properties when not chained into',73,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
