('30b9af38-0cbd-4276-88b2-d4b450689841','Ken','Stand MK','','5MK','normal',8,3,20,-5,3,600,'H','tc','Whiffs on crouch from further ranges; Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo; Ken lifts up his front leg hurtbox on frames 4-15 making this a good tool against low attacks; Has a hit confirmable (19F) MK > MK > HK Target Combo follow-up (combos even at max range stand MK)',5,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('d9f5f7ad-6699-4418-ac57-2c0e35dbbb61','Ken','Stand HK','','5HK','normal',12,2,23,-5,1,800,'H','','Good range poke (slightly further range than stand MK) with solid follow-up juggles on Punish; The brief extended leg hurtbox on frame 11 of start-up (1F before active) is strike invincible (cannot counter-poke projectiles); +2F extra recovery frames (25F) on whiff only; Incurs 30% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo',6,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('212e9676-996a-4fb3-bd8c-833e283ca00e','Ken','Crouch LP','','2LP','normal',4,2,9,-1,5,300,'H','ch, sp, su','Chains into stand LP / crouch LP / crouch LK; Important combo tool as it combos naturally into the MP > HP Target Combo; Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo; Topmost hurtboxes on frames 1-5 are vulnerable only to airborne attacks (this is to discourage its use as an anti-air)',7,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('68c9ce5e-eab7-4677-a46a-feb523c477b5','Ken','Crouch MP','','2MP','normal',6,3,14,0,3,700,'H','sp, su','Great combo / poke / buffer / pressure tool; Topmost hurtboxes on frames 1-8 are vulnerable only to airborne attacks (this is to discourage its use as an anti-air); +2 extra recovery frames (16F) on whiff only',8,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
