('6f5af2dd-cb97-4582-a0eb-521f09978be7','Kimberly','Water Slicer Slide [Super Install]','','3MK','normal',11,10,16,-5,1,499,'L','','Incredibly strong tool to bypass many projectiles even on reaction and getting combo conversions on Punish Counter; Low profile and projectile invincible on upper body on frames 9-21; Puts airborne opponents into a limited juggle state; Incurs a 15% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo; The first 4 active frames have a set minimum advantage on hit and block (some remaining active frames are skipped to leave Kimberly +1 on Hit / -5 on Block); These 4 active frames also cause a knockdown on Punish Counter (great for punishing whiffed attacks, slow close-range projectiles, or some sweeps with high pushback)',99,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('e8324ddb-e619-4ced-8594-9c6dc7b32580','Kimberly','Windmill Kick [Super Install]','','4HK','normal',22,2,19,-3,4,799,'M','','Overhead; Forces crouch on hit; Safe on block overhead that she can combo from naturally; Spike knockdown on airborne opponents; Incurs 25% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo',100,datetime('now'),datetime('now'));
