('c43b9095-35cf-44ab-a5f6-a3171a366fad','Kimberly','OD Sprint > Torso Cleaver [Super Install]','','236KK > LK','special',8,7,16,3,NULL,1198,'H','su2, su3','Extended legs are invincible to airborne strikes on frames 14-23 (not including the initial 8F of Run start-up); Cannot hit cross-up (behind Kimberly); Whiffs on grounded opponents on active frames 3-7 (hits the air above Kimberly then); Puts opponents into a limited juggle state; Cancelable into Level 2 and 3 Supers on Hit and Block',129,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('59ea6d37-e53e-4eca-9c8d-18f05a235e91','Kimberly','OD Sprint > Shadow Slide [Super Install]','','236KK > MK','special',8,8,19,-10,NULL,999,'L','su2, su3','Projectile Invincible (except on the extended leg) on frames 4-19 (not including the 8F of Run start-up); Low hitting slide that puts opponent into a limited juggle state; First hit forces stand (allows SA2 cancel to combo consistently); Cancelable into Level 2 and 3 Supers on Hit and Block; Incurs a 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo',130,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
