('6fb06080-e0d6-4894-99cc-2540cc73ddbf','Kimberly','OD Sprint > Arc Step [Super Install]','','236KK (proximity)','special',8,2,26,-6,3,298,'H','','Can only hit grounded opponents; Airborne on frames 20-54F (4F grounded recovery frames); Kimberly whiffs her proximity attack if the opponent goes airborne during the start-up of the proximity triggered attack (13F start-up); 25F recovery is the proximity attack whiffs on an airborne opponent; Can frametrap 4F normals when canceled from stand HP / stand MP / stand MK / Bushin Tiger Fangs (true blockstring from crouch HP); Isn''t automatically performed if Kimberly is holding forward (Classic) or SP (Modern) while she''s running forward; When juggled from Bushin Tiger Fangs, puts the opponent into a limited juggle state (allows a midscreen combo into LP Elbow or Level 1/3 Super); Kimberly becomes airborne immediately after being Perfect Parried (opponent must punish with up to a 6F Forced Knockdown or anti-air invincible attack)',132,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('e7cc0bd2-44c0-4b35-af37-0aaccc1eb9b2','Kimberly','OD Arc Step > Bushin Hojin Kick [Super Install]','','236KK (proximity) > K','special',8,6,20,-8,NULL,997,'H','su2','Not an Overhead; Knockdown that also causes a wall splat when opponent is close enough to the wall (+43 KDA normally but +86 on a Wall Splat); Cancelable into Level 2 Super (air version) on both hits; Second attack only occurs on hit; Forced Knockdown state while airborne; Can frametrap 4F normals when canceled from crouch HP / stand HP / stand MP',133,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('4c1b9ea2-4104-447d-98d4-9d2f124262bc','Kimberly','OD Arc Step > Bushin Izuna Otoshi [Super Install]','','236KK (proximity) > P','special',8,6,40,NULL,NULL,999,'T','','Grabs standing and crouch; Cannot grab airborne opponents; Puts opponent into an OTG juggleable state; Forced Knockdown state while airborne; Counts as two hits of damage scaling if used as a combo starter',134,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('125865b7-14cf-428f-b56d-011a0aa5e35f','Kimberly','Shuriken Bomb [Super Install]','','22P (1 stock)','special',18,10,26,NULL,NULL,499,'H','','Kimberly places a Spray Can on frame 18 that explodes after 122F (LP/L) | 124F (MP/M) | 128F (HP/H) total frames; Strength of the button dictates where Kimberly places her explosive Spray Can (Close: LP (Classic) / L (Modern) | Mid-screen: MP (Classic) / M (Modern) | Full-screen: HP (Classic) / H (Modern)); Kimberly can only have two active Spray Cans on screen at a time; Kimberly cannot re-stock on her Spray Cans until she has depleted her current stock (she also can''t re-stock on her Spray Cans while another Spray Can is currently active/armed on screen); Incurs 10% damage scaling if used as the first hit of a combo; The explosion launches the opponent into a free juggle state on hit (limited juggle state if it hits mid-combo); The explosion can even OTG the opponent in some scenarios; Very strong oki tool with lots of pressure and mix-up potential',135,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('a86147fe-4746-46e8-ac50-af3f768e4882','Kimberly','Shuriken Bomb Spread [Super Install]','','22PP (2 stock)','special',18,10,26,NULL,NULL,998,'H','','Kimberly places two different Spray Cans on frame 18 whose overall explosion start-up depends on their button strength; 122F (LP) | 124F (MP) | 128F (HP) total frames; Strength of the punch button (LP/MP/HP) dictates where Kimberly places her explosive Spray Can (Close: LP | Mid-screen: MP | Full-screen: HP); Kimberly can only have two active Spray Cans on screen at a time; Kimberly cannot re-stock on her Spray Cans until she has depleted her current stock (she also can''t re-stock on her Spray Cans while another Spray Can is currently active/armed on screen); Incurs 10% damage scaling if used as the first hit of a combo; The explosions launch the opponent into a free juggle state on hit (limited juggle state if it hits mid-combo); The explosion can even OTG the opponent in some scenarios; Very strong oki tool with lots of pressure and mix-up potential',136,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
