('57095f8a-1c0d-4275-8dc9-742db298b707','Luke','LP Sand Blast','','236LP','special',14,5,33,-8,-3,600,'H','su3','1-hit projectile; Projectile Speed: 0.12 (active frames 1-2) | 0.42 (active frames 3+); Travels 45% screen length; Extended arm hurtbox is projectile invincible on frames 13-37',37,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('7c362ea0-30ab-4767-aee1-ea29ff381ad6','Luke','MP Sand Blast','','236MP','special',17,7,30,-5,0,600,'H','su3','1-hit projectile; Projectile Speed: 0.12 (active frames 1-2) | 0.42 (active frames 3+); Travels 65% screen length; Extended arm hurtbox is projectile invincible on frames 16-39',38,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('b7a13299-7a7c-4095-8315-6731d6c3fee3','Luke','HP Sand Blast','','236HP','special',20,10,27,-2,3,600,'H','su3','1-hit projectile; Projectile Speed: 0.12 (active frames 1-2) | 0.42 (active frames 3+); Travels 90% screen length; Extended arm hurtbox is projectile invincible on frames 19-41',39,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('60133f79-4c36-4977-b7a8-0479c02912f0','Luke','OD Sand Blast','','236PP','special',16,NULL,24,-2,NULL,800,'H','su2, su3','2-hit OD projectile; Projectile Speed: 0.12 (active frames 1-2) | 0.42 (active frames 3+); Travels full-screen; Can be followed up with Fatal Shot (PP) for another 1 bar of Drive Gauge; Extended arm hurtbox on frames 19-36 is projectile invincible; Puts the opponent into a limited juggle state on hit; Counts as 2 hits of damage scaling',40,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('164c050e-7d0f-46c9-bdb1-47c0a21ea9ba','Luke','Fatal Shot','','236PP > PP','special',8,NULL,42,-21,NULL,1000,'H','','1-hit OD projectile; Projectile Speed: 0.2; Travels full-screen; Extended arm hurtbox is projectile invincible on frames 10-32; This extension deals a 1000 damage by itself (800 damage if combo''d into from OD Sand Blast); Causes a short wallsplat on hit (can get juggle follow-ups near the corner, or whiff Avenger > No Chaser to gain ground)',41,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('082cbfcb-3070-4802-a419-bc148d08573e','Luke','LP Rising Uppercut','','623LP','special',5,10,22,-27,NULL,900,'H','su3','Invincible against airborne strikes on frames 1-14; Airborne on frames 7-36 (Forced Knockdown state); Deals 100 less damage (800) on active frames 3-10; Much higher juggle limit compared to other versions of Rising Uppercut (increased even further on active frames 3-10); Cannot hit cross-up (behind Luke)',42,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('c1cf0a3c-0fa5-4bc1-85c5-3e2bdf5cb641','Luke','MP Rising Uppercut','','623MP','special',6,10,24,-29,NULL,1000,'H','su3','Invincible against airborne strikes on frames 1-8; Airborne on frames 8-39 (Forced Knockdown state); Deals 200 less damage (800) on active frames 3-10; Cannot hit cross-up (behind Luke)',43,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('85725b9f-dff0-4b53-bd2f-589c19b591fb','Luke','HP Rising Uppercut','','623HP','special',9,10,25,-33,NULL,1200,'H','su3','Invincible against airborne strikes on frames 1-9; Airborne on frames 11-43 (Forced Knockdown state); Deals 400 less damage (800) on active frames 2-10; Cannot hit cross-up (behind Luke)',44,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('2fb12905-f031-456c-8d23-94d48a0706eb','Luke','OD Rising Uppercut','','623PP','special',6,3,35,-40,NULL,1400,'H','','Fully invincible on frames 1-10; Airborne on frames 8-50 (Forced Knockdown state); First hit deals 200 less damage (600) on third active frame (for a total of 1200 damage with the second hit); Second hit whiffs on crouch block (-43 on block); Cannot hit cross-up (behind Luke)',45,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('e1db7a40-893d-4208-bb0b-63040038589b','Luke','Slam Dunk','','623PP > PP','special',16,3,14,NULL,NULL,2000,'H','','Follow-up to OD Rising Uppercut at the cost of 1 extra bar of Drive Gauge; Counts as a follow-up hit in terms of damage scaling',46,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('fcdaf46a-e09d-4e98-bf11-c08004a349a7','Luke','LP Flash Knuckle','','214LP','special',13,3,31,-18,NULL,700,'H','su3','Luke ducks down (no head hurtbox) on frames 6-17 (good anti-air hitboxes but a bit slow for anti-airing); Puts opponent into a limited juggle state on hit',47,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('2826a5e2-41b1-480b-bbb0-f823bc21bc57','Luke','LP Flash Knuckle (hold)','','214LP (hold)','special',26,2,25,-8,NULL,800,'H','su3','Luke ducks down (no head hurtbox) on frames 6-29; Has a normal 1-hit projectile nullifying hitbox (does not nullify OD or Super projectiles) on active frames 3-4; Launches the opponent high into a limited juggle state on hit; LP button must be released between frames 18-20 of start-up in order to get the Perfect version; Perfect version has +100 (900) damage, 3F less recovery, and +2 KDA; Framedata shown in parentheses refers to the Perfect version; Counts as 2 hits of damage scaling',48,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('9ef10ff9-5ec5-494f-a467-22cf6aea2887','Luke','MP Flash Knuckle','','214MP','special',19,3,27,-8,3,900,'H','su3','Knocks airborne opponents far away into a limited juggle state; Can usually be spaced safely against opponents in Burnout',49,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('52db5a4e-5f0d-4057-9adf-ff3ec7c2784c','Luke','MP Flash Knuckle (hold)','','214MP (hold)','special',29,2,26,-3,NULL,1000,'H','su3','Launches the opponent into a wall bounce; Has a normal 1-hit projectile nullifying hitbox (does not nullify OD or Super projectiles) on active frames 3-4; MP button must be released between frames 18-20 of start-up in order to get the Perfect version; Perfect version has +100 (1100) damage, 1F faster start-up, but -1 KDA; Both Perfect and non-Perfect versions can be combo''d into from crouch HP; KDA varies greatly depending on how close the opponent is to the wall when hit (higher KDA the further away the wall is upon impact); Counts as 2 hits of damage scaling on the non-Perfect version only',50,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('685e8483-cb2f-432a-b6e8-43285cd79216','Luke','HP Flash Knuckle','','214HP','special',22,3,21,-4,NULL,1000,'H','su3','Luke pulls back his hurtboxes on frames 5-15 during start-up (can avoid attacks with this); Puts opponent into a limited juggle state on hit; Has less KDA against airborne opponents (+31 KD after LP~MP~HP for example)',51,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('a4e08ee0-ab4e-4681-87e6-e8e6686def99','Luke','HP Flash Knuckle (hold)','','214HP (hold)','special',33,2,24,4,NULL,1300,'H','su3','Has a normal 1-hit projectile nullifying hitbox (does not nullify OD or Super projectiles) on active frames 3-4; HP button must be released between frames 18-20 of start-up in order to get the Perfect version; Perfect version has +300 (1600) damage; Counts as 2 hits of damage scaling; Luke pulls back his hurtboxes on frame 5 and onward during start-up (up to frame 25 if fully held)',52,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('3cb1ce37-d3b0-4c4c-8773-729845c977af','Luke','OD Flash Knuckle','','214PP','special',15,3,39,-22,NULL,800,'H','su2, su3','Launches the opponent high into a limited juggle state on hit; Has a normal 1-hit projectile nullifying hitbox (does not nullify OD or Super projectiles) on active frames 3-4; Recovery frames listed refers to the version that plays out on block and whiff (follow-up only comes out on hit); Can be followed up with DDT (PP input) for another 1 bar of Drive Gauge (this only comes out if the opponent is low enough to the ground)',53,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('1ee03650-9c83-4368-837f-9ef614610734','Luke','DDT','','214PP > PP','special',1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,2900,'H','','Hard Knockdown follow-up to OD Flash Knuckle at the cost of 1 extra bar of Drive Gauge; Counts as a follow-up hit in terms of damage scaling; Only comes out if the opponent is low enough to the ground when OD Flash Knuckle hits',54,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('1f51c3cf-a3ad-4810-bf4f-d31fe72ac568','Luke','Aerial Flash Knuckle','','214P (air)','special',14,5,13,-12,NULL,700,'H','','Can only be performed during a neutral or forward jump (can also be performed on a back jump if canceling into this from a jump MP); +7 extra landing recovery frames (20F) if used at the apex of the jump; All landing recovery after the first 3 frames is in a crouching state; Forced Knockdown state while airborne; At best up to -1 on block from up close (but can be up to +3 on block when spaced out from further ranges so the last active frame connects on block)',55,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('6ac17b9d-06c6-4080-a77d-aa603400541d','Luke','Aerial Flash Knuckle (hold)','','214P (air) (hold)','special',23,6,15,-30,NULL,1000,'H','','Can only be performed during a neutral or forward jump (can also be performed on a back jump if canceling into this from a jump MP); Puts the opponent into a limited juggle state (Luke can juggle afterwards if it hits the opponent high enough in the air); 15F landing recovery frames of which the majority (12F) is in a crouching state; Forced Knockdown state while airborne',56,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('f48375c4-aa4e-48cf-b9a5-050ab2d48909','Luke','OD Aerial Flash Knuckle','','214PP (air)','special',14,6,15,-33,NULL,1300,'H','','Can only be performed during a neutral or forward jump (can also be performed on a back jump if canceling into this from a jump MP); Puts the opponent into a limited juggle state; All landing recovery after the first 3 frames is in a crouching state; Forced Knockdown state while airborne',57,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('c2384a9f-e634-4a86-92ab-3731cbcb73b1','Luke','Avenger','','236K','special',12,NULL,33,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','Cancels into follow-ups on frames 12-32; Luke is in a Counter-Hit state during the run',58,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('14918a5d-e6c4-4544-aa60-75f6b53bb5eb','Luke','Avenger > No Chaser','','236K > P','special',12,10,16,-6,NULL,900,'H','su3','Tons of active frames makes this a strong tool for oki to set up + frames on block; Puts the opponent into a limited juggle state',59,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('3031e1c3-1bf0-46c3-8d75-1bf56410dd5d','Luke','Avenger > Impaler','','236K > K','special',12,8,22,-8,NULL,1200,'M','','Overhead; First two active frames can only hit airborne opponents; Airborne on frames 4-19 (frames 16-31 if you include the minimum Run start-up prior); Forced Knockdown state while airborne; Kicking leg hurtbox is invincible to airborne strikes on frames 12-14; Crouching state for the entire recovery frames; Knockdown advantage varies depending on what active frames it hits; Puts the opponent into a limited juggle state',60,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('7a3282b0-afcb-4e98-bd37-2e006bc84cab','Luke','OD Avenger','','236KK','special',11,33,10,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','Has one hit of armor on frames 3-35 (the armor does not carry through into the follow-ups); Cancels into follow-ups on frames 11-32; Luke is in a Punish Counter state during the run (armor break or throw); Active frames listed refers to the armor duration',61,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('a33de385-0f75-4ba7-8c44-62bd0f9996c1','Luke','OD Avenger > No Chaser','','236KK > P','special',11,10,16,-6,NULL,1300,'H','su2, su3','Tons of active frames makes this a strong tool for oki to set up + frames on block; Puts the opponent into a limited juggle state; Incurs 50% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo',62,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('ab6cb34a-363b-459d-aba0-42946eb7d223','Luke','OD Avenger > Impaler','','236KK > K','special',11,8,19,-3,NULL,1200,'M','','Overhead; First two active frames can only hit airborne opponents; Airborne on frames 4-19 (frames 16-31 if you include the minimum Run start-up prior); Forced Knockdown state while airborne; Kicking leg hurtbox is invincible to airborne strikes on frames 12-14; Crouching state for the entire recovery frames; Knockdown advantage varies depending on what active frames it hits; Puts the opponent into a limited juggle state; Incurs 50% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo',63,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('62d735bf-1a32-4711-8147-210efc537f10','Luke','Vulcan Blast','','236236P','super',6,13,45,-29,NULL,2000,'H','','Strike and Throw invincible on frames 1-6; 5-hit projectile; Only the last hit travels full-screen (first 4 hits go about 65% screen length); KDA varies greatly depending on the opponents distance from the wall (higher KDA the further away Luke blasts them); Armor Break; Depletes 0.5 Drive Bar on hit for the opponent; Fantastic punish and anti-projectile tool from over half-screen away',64,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('827af5ca-5328-4528-b628-58c8e8307b97','Luke','Eraser','','214214P','super',5,3,51,-29,NULL,2800,'H','','Fully invincible on frames 1-7 (loses invincibility after the initial hit before the cinematic punch at the end); Armor Break; Depletes 1 Drive Bar on hit for the opponent; Leaves Luke up close for a strike / throw mix-up in the corner',65,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('10540bc1-eed8-4e61-9bdc-7f154f3e7b29','Luke','Pale Rider','','236236K','super',10,4,92,-42,NULL,4000,'H','','Fully invincible on frames 1-13; Start-up is based on the proximity range to the opponent (up to 27F from max range); Hits both grounded and airborne opponents; Armor Break; Depletes 1.5 Drive Bars on hit for the opponent; Super cinematic time regenerates ~2 Drive Bars for Luke; Incurs 10% damage scaling when canceled into from specials; Recovery / Total frames listed refers to the version that plays out on whiff (30F less recovery frames on block)',66,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('289dc026-0026-4c4f-85ce-5866b043e4f0','Luke','Pale Rider (Critical Art)','','236236K (CA)','super',10,4,92,-42,NULL,4500,'H','','Fully invincible on frames 1-13; Start-up is based on the proximity range to the opponent (up to 27F from max range); Hits both grounded and airborne opponents; Critical Art does +500 extra damage over regular version; Armor Break; Depletes 2 Drive Bars on hit for the opponent; Super cinematic time regenerates ~2.3 Drive Bars for Luke; Incurs 10% damage scaling when canceled into from specials; Recovery / Total frames listed refers to the version that plays out on whiff (30F less recovery frames on block)',67,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('a251a52e-49db-4280-a0e6-1f9eb963d12b','M. Bison','Stand LP','','5LP','normal',5,2,11,-3,4,300,'H','ch, sp, su','Good range for a jab; Chains into stand LP / crouch LP / crouch LK; Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo',1,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('7cf5eeb5-7a94-47e5-b954-bc59c9584e4b','M. Bison','Stand MP','','5MP','normal',8,3,15,0,6,600,'H','sp, su, tc','Primary combo / frametrap tool which also leads into Overhead / Low Target Combo follow-ups',2,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('59ade5eb-62ee-4245-96ca-084eb17052ce','M. Bison','Stand HP','','5HP','normal',19,3,17,1,4,1000,'H','su','A slow advancing poke with good range and hitbox priority as well as + frames on block; Slams down airborne opponents into a limited OTG juggle state on hit (only combos into Super cancels on Hit / Counter Hit), with an extended knockdown timer on Punish Counter (more juggle follow-ups possible); The brief extended hurtbox on frame 18 of start-up (1F before active) is strike invincible (cannot counter-poke projectiles); Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo; +3F extra recovery (20F) on whiff or when absorbed by armor',3,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('f99807e2-0e00-479e-84db-6818a623d7a7','M. Bison','Stand LK','','5LK','normal',4,2,10,-1,3,300,'H','sp, su','Primary combo tool from lights since it moves Dictator forward for the follow-up cancel / combo; +1 on block when Drive Rush canceling from this move, despite being a light attack (light attacks are usually never + on block during Drive Rush cancels); Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo',4,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('1fac0222-38db-49d8-8bdd-f0bb64190dd1','M. Bison','Stand MK','','5MK','normal',10,3,17,-3,2,700,'H','','Great poke tool with good range and hitbox priority',5,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('c078eb68-b12f-4959-99eb-be7e8827dceb','M. Bison','Stand HK','','5HK','normal',13,4,19,-2,6,900,'H','','Solid but slow anti-air option as well as a combo tool; Whiffs on crouching opponents from further away; Punish Counter Crumple is +7 before the crumple state goes airborne; Puts airborne opponents into a limited juggle state (much higher launch on Punish Counter); Extended foot hurtbox is invincible to airborne strikes on frames 13-16; The brief extended leg hurtbox on frame 12 of start-up (1F before active) is strike invincible (cannot counter-poke projectiles)',6,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('a136dc3d-4a32-4fa5-a136-93033c3d8a0f','M. Bison','Crouch LP','','2LP','normal',4,2,10,-2,4,300,'H','ch, sp, su','Chains into stand LP / crouch LP / crouch LK; Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo; Topmost hurtboxes on frames 1-5 are vulnerable only to airborne attacks (this is to discourage its use as an anti-air)',7,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('2554eb73-b564-452a-8a6e-8ece60e15a86','M. Bison','Crouch MP','','2MP','normal',6,3,14,-1,5,600,'H','sp, su','Very good range for a 6F Crouch MP; Solid combo and buffer tool; +3F extra recovery (17F) on whiff; Topmost hurtboxes on frames 1-8 are vulnerable only to airborne attacks (this is to discourage its use as an anti-air)',8,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('65a1fb03-7ee6-433e-9b8f-30997f6a27e8','M. Bison','Crouch HP','','2HP','normal',10,6,21,-9,0,900,'H','sp, su','Forces stand on hit; Slow anti-air with very strong anti-air hitbox priority on frames 12-15 but cannot hit cross-up (behind M. Bison); Launches airborne opponents into a limited juggle state on Counter-Hit / Punish Counter; Only cancelable on the first 2 active frames',9,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('3c2cee68-4c4c-4072-a3e7-ce7fae587d3c','M. Bison','Crouch LK','','2LK','normal',5,2,10,-2,4,200,'L','ch','Chains into stand LP / crouch LP / crouch LK; Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo; Rare crouch LK that is +4 on hit and links naturally into other lights',10,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('1a71da6d-3528-4cd5-bd3b-17586a4a92eb','M. Bison','Crouch MK','','2MK','normal',8,3,19,-6,-2,500,'L','sp, su','Pretty standard special cancelable crouch MK; Extends a wide hurtbox through the first 9 recovery frames; Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo',11,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('79ebee32-467a-47d1-8d53-10e502dd8d31','M. Bison','Crouch HK','','2HK','normal',11,3,26,-12,NULL,900,'L','','Good range and hitbox priority; Has some Juggle potential naturally without Drive Rush; Not a Hard Knockdown (HKD) when juggled into; Puts airborne opponents into a limited juggle state (can lead into combo extensions with a well timed Psycho Mine detonation)',12,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('03c76b4f-0add-4db3-852c-b92cc30227b5','M. Bison','Jump LP','','8LP','normal',5,4,NULL,4,8,300,'M','','Decent air-to-air',13,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('a347ef64-4635-48fa-a0ae-80dddbfe2371','M. Bison','Jump MP','','8MP','normal',8,4,NULL,5,9,700,'M','tc','Puts airborne opponents into a limited juggle state; Great air-to-air with a long cancel window into the Hell Attack target combo; Shifts Dictator''s hurtboxes slightly upwards during start-up',14,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('ec642f84-25e4-449d-801f-379d05af73c2','M. Bison','Jump HP','','8HP','normal',9,6,NULL,3,7,800,'M','','Spikes down airborne opponents on Counter-Hit or Punish Counter; Solid hitboxes for a vertical approach',15,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('991faf3f-5e86-4215-8617-7536a1b85f0e','M. Bison','Jump LK','','8LK','normal',5,7,NULL,3,7,300,'M','','Cross-up; Decent air-to-air',16,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('a2a6e02d-dd51-4718-b5da-f30f47cae5df','M. Bison','Jump MK','','8MK','normal',7,7,NULL,5,9,500,'M','','Cross-up; Shifts Dictator''s hurtboxes slightly upwards during start-up',17,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('ac45ae13-b5b0-408f-ac3a-6cbc5a441a3e','M. Bison','Jump HK','','8HK','normal',10,6,NULL,7,11,800,'M','','Furthest horizontal range of Dictator''s jump normals',18,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('887c223a-de97-4a3d-a7a2-4c1307ab47a2','M. Bison','Hell Attack','','8MP > 8MP','normal',7,4,NULL,NULL,NULL,700,'H','','Both hits put airborne opponents into a limited juggle state',19,datetime('now'),datetime('now'));
