('14f6f982-c9c4-49f4-9569-34a211089caa','Mai','LP Ryuuenbu','','214LP','special',14,7,15,-4,3,800,'H','su3','Strike hitbox that also can also nullify 1 hit of a non-OD projectile; This LP version doesn''t knockdown on normal hit like the other versions, instead gives good frame advantage on hit (+3) to maintain pressure; KD +35 on Counter-Hit or Punish Counter; Can be spaced out to be relatively safe on block; Decent oki tool due to lots of active frames (up to +9 on hit / +2 on block)',54,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('54893179-d087-43d3-a261-005e8a41be52','Mai','LP Ryuuenbu (stock)','','214LP (stock)','special',14,7,15,-2,NULL,900,'H','su3','Enhanced: +100 damage (900 damage total), safe on block (-2 instead of -4), and knocks down on normal hit (Knockdown doesn''t require Counter-Hit or Punish Counter); Strike hitbox that also can also nullify 1 hit of a non-OD projectile; Can be spaced out to be relatively safe on block; Decent oki tool due to lots of active frames (up to +4 on block)',55,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('06210a95-faf7-4761-bbbd-a1cd3e1dfc0a','Mai','MP Ryuuenbu','','214MP','special',14,2,16,-6,NULL,1000,'H','su3','Strike hitbox that also can also nullify 1 hit of a non-OD projectile on the second hit; Can be spaced out to be relatively safe on block; Very similar to the normal LP version with the same startup, but knocks down on normal hit (does not require a Counter-Hit / Punish Counter or Flame Stock to cause a knockdown); Cancelable into SA3 on the second hit',56,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('689e0d8f-0e24-4029-b32a-ab001203d0fc','Mai','MP Ryuuenbu (stock)','','214MP (stock)','special',14,2,16,-6,NULL,1100,'H','su3','Enhanced: +100 damage (1100 damage total) and better oki (KD +42 instead of KD +35); Strike hitbox that also can also nullify 1 hit of a non-OD projectile on the second hit; Can be spaced out to be relatively safe on block; Very similar to the normal LP version with the same startup, but knocks down on normal hit (does not require a Counter-Hit / Punish Counter or Flame Stock to cause a knockdown); Counts as 2 hits of damage scaling when used in the middle of a combo',57,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('512c6f03-a260-40ba-94e5-3bb5d5cf2668','Mai','HP Ryuuenbu','','214HP','special',15,3,12,-6,NULL,800,'H','su3','Head hurtbox is invincible to airborne strikes on frames 6-17 (situational but slow anti-air option); Strike hitbox that also can also nullify 1 hit of a non-OD projectile on the second hit; Cannot hit crouching opponents (only combo into this when the opponent is standing); Second hit launches the opponent up high for a follow-up juggle; Cancelable into SA3 on the second hit; Counts as 2 hits of damage scaling when used in the middle of a combo',58,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('ff2ab170-589d-4d26-b9ab-4d48a38d3cd1','Mai','HP Ryuuenbu (stock)','','214HP (stock)','special',15,3,12,-6,NULL,900,'H','su3','Enhanced: +100 damage (900 damage total), no additional damage scaling, and better juggles / oki (KD +47 instead of KD +43); Head hurtbox is invincible to airborne strikes on frames 6-17 (situational but slow anti-air option); Strike hitbox that also can also nullify 1 hit of a non-OD projectile on the second hit; Cannot hit crouching opponents (only combo into this when the opponent is standing); Second hit launches the opponent up high for a follow-up juggle',59,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('650b6f3c-be4f-4ed3-9a92-0269cd372441','Mai','OD Ryuuenbu','','214PP','special',16,2,16,-12,NULL,1000,'H','su2, su3','Strike hitbox that can also nullify 1 hit of OD projectile on the second and third hit; Last hit launches the opponent up high for juggle follow-ups (free juggle state if only the last hit connected); Cancelable into SA2/SA3 on the last hit; +8F extra recovery frames (24F) on block',60,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('de58dea9-f74d-4928-8550-a71e1ab1db65','Mai','OD Ryuuenbu (stock)','','214PP (stock)','special',16,2,16,-12,NULL,1100,'H','su2, su3','Enhanced: +100 damage (1100 damage total) and better juggle routes (Juggle Increase +1 instead of +2); Strike hitbox that can also nullify 1 hit of OD projectile on the second and third hit; Last hit launches the opponent up high for juggle follow-ups (free juggle state if only the last hit connected); Cancelable into SA2/SA3 on the last hit; +8F extra recovery frames (24F) on block',61,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('ed3f081f-29b8-46f0-9ade-6ba4cc07c005','Mai','LK Hissatsu Shinobi Bachi','','236LK','special',10,2,16,-10,NULL,800,'H','su3','Core combo tool with fantastic corner carry; Puts the opponent into a limited juggle state (sets up for juggle follow-ups in various airborne juggle scenarios); Reaches about 80% screen length (can be very plus on block if spaced properly or used as meaty oki tool); Second hit (elbow) whiffs on crouching opponents on active frames 7-13 but hits them again on active frames 14-17 (this means Mai can be interrupted by some crouching attacks but it''s also easier to space for + frames against crouching opponents); Only second hit is cancelable into SA3',62,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('52a6c19f-878e-45ee-96f7-209b21a48326','Mai','LK Hissatsu Shinobi Bachi (stock)','','236LK (stock)','special',10,2,16,-10,NULL,900,'H','su3','Enhanced: +100 extra damage on the second hit (900 damage total); Core combo tool with fantastic corner carry; Puts the opponent into a limited juggle state (sets up for juggle follow-ups in various airborne juggle scenarios); Reaches about 80% screen length (can be very plus on block if spaced properly); Second hit (elbow) whiffs on crouching opponents on active frames 7-13 but hits them again on active frames 14-17 (this means Mai can be interrupted by some crouching attacks but it''s also easier to space for + frames against crouching opponents); Only second hit is cancelable into SA3',63,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('2fef1fc1-2f75-4f1f-a579-e27732841c7a','Mai','MK Hissatsu Shinobi Bachi','','236MK','special',15,2,20,-12,NULL,900,'H','su3','Core combo tool with fantastic corner carry; Puts the opponent into a limited juggle state (sets up for juggle follow-ups in various airborne juggle scenarios); Reaches about 99% screen length (just barely whiffs on standing opponents; up to +4 on block if spaced from full-screen or used as meaty oki tool); Second hit (elbow) whiffs on crouching opponents on active frames 7-15 but hits them again on active frames 16-17 (this means Mai can be interrupted by some crouching attacks but it''s also easier to space for + frames against crouching opponents); Only second hit is cancelable into SA3',64,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('7fdbfbc3-4834-4567-a873-672234d17edb','Mai','MK Hissatsu Shinobi Bachi (stock)','','236MK (stock)','special',15,2,20,-12,NULL,1000,'H','su3','Enhanced: +100 extra damage on second hit (1000 damage total); Core combo tool with fantastic corner carry; Puts the opponent into a limited juggle state (sets up for juggle follow-ups in various airborne juggle scenarios); Reaches about 99% screen length (just barely whiffs on standing opponents; up to +4 on block if spaced from full-screen or used as meaty oki tool); Second hit (elbow) whiffs on crouching opponents on active frames 7-15 but hits them again on active frames 16-17 (this means Mai can be interrupted by some crouching attacks but it''s also easier to space for + frames against crouching opponents); Only second hit is cancelable into SA3',65,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('dab412b9-14fa-4ba3-a32d-69b392142319','Mai','HK Hissatsu Shinobi Bachi','','236HK','special',18,2,21,-13,NULL,1000,'H','su3','Core combo tool with fantastic corner carry; Puts the opponent into a limited juggle state (sets up for juggle follow-ups in various airborne juggle scenarios); Reaches beyond full-screen length (up to +2~3 on block if spaced from full-screen against crouching opponents or used as meaty oki tool); Second hit (elbow) whiffs on crouching opponents on active frames 7-15 but hits them again on active frames 16-17 (this means Mai can be interrupted by some crouching attacks but it''s also easier to space for + frames against crouching opponents); Only second hit is cancelable into SA3',66,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('968f3cd2-4b25-4e51-a19d-473e85b2a75a','Mai','HK Hissatsu Shinobi Bachi (stock)','','236HK (stock)','special',18,2,21,-13,NULL,1100,'H','su3','Enhanced: +100 extra damage on second hit (1100 damage total); Core combo tool with fantastic corner carry; Puts the opponent into a limited juggle state (sets up for juggle follow-ups in various airborne juggle scenarios); Reaches beyond full-screen length (up to +2~3 on block if spaced from full-screen against crouching opponents or used as meaty oki tool); Second hit (elbow) whiffs on crouching opponents on active frames 7-15 but hits them again on active frames 16-17 (this means Mai can be interrupted by some crouching attacks but it''s also easier to space for + frames against crouching opponents); Only second hit is cancelable into SA3',67,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('d029c602-d55e-485e-b4be-df7643cdd762','Mai','OD Hissatsu Shinobi Bachi','','236KK','special',14,2,29,-12,NULL,800,'H','su2, su3','Can be followed-up with airborne normals / specials on frames 54-74 (air follow-ups are not possible on block); Mai does not leap into the air if the initial cartweel is blocked; Airborne on frames 31-74 (Forced Knockdown state) followed by 3F landing recovery if no follow-up is performed in the air; Second hit (elbow) cannot hit grounded opponents beyond the first active frame; Only second hit is cancelable into SA2/SA3 (usually better to delay the SA2 cancel here for the airborne version)',68,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('bfff94ac-f084-4a99-b644-44972fc89f11','Mai','OD Hissatsu Shinobi Bachi (stock)','','236KK (stock)','special',14,2,29,-12,NULL,900,'H','su2, su3','Enhanced: +100 extra damage on second hit (900 damage total); Can be followed-up with airborne normals / specials on frames 54-74 (air follow-ups are not possible on block); Mai does not leap into the air if the initial cartweel is blocked; Airborne on frames 31-74 (Forced Knockdown state) followed by 3F landing recovery if no follow-up is performed in the air; Second hit (elbow) cannot hit grounded opponents beyond the first active frame; Only second hit is cancelable into SA2/SA3 (usually better to delay the SA2 cancel here for the airborne version)',69,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('b89447bb-a71d-455f-9333-c0463bcb2bca','Mai','Musasabi no Mai','','214P (air)','special',21,NULL,18,-8,NULL,1000,'H','','Can only be performed during a forward jump; Puts the opponent into a limited juggle state on hit; Forced Knockdown state while airborne; Solid hitbox for a divekick but rather slow start-up and long landing recovery frames; +10F extra recovery frames (28F) on whiff when landing behind the opponent; Crouching state on the final landing recovery frame',70,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('31104dde-a6d9-468f-8be2-ad2bf642f439','Mai','Musasabi no Mai (stock)','','214P (stock + air)','special',21,NULL,18,-5,NULL,1100,'H','','Enhanced: +100 damage (1100 damage total) and slightly better frame advantage on hit / block; Can only be performed during a forward jump; Puts the opponent into a limited juggle state on hit; Forced Knockdown state while airborne; Solid hitbox for a divekick but rather slow start-up and long landing recovery frames; +10F extra recovery frames (28F) on whiff when landing behind the opponent; Crouching state on the final landing recovery frame',71,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('b0dc7128-bcfd-4d4c-a0fb-f5a5112259d0','Mai','OD Musasabi no Mai','','214PP (air)','special',21,NULL,18,-8,NULL,1200,'H','su2','Can only be performed during a forward jump; Puts the opponent into a limited juggle state on hit (more juggle potential than the non-OD version); Forced Knockdown state while airborne; Solid hitbox for a divekick but rather slow start-up and long landing recovery frames; +10F extra recovery frames (28F) on whiff when landing behind the opponent; Crouching state on the final landing recovery frame',72,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('7231c350-ab31-441e-ba38-7f7f5704487b','Mai','OD Musasabi no Mai (stock)','','214PP (stock + air)','special',21,NULL,18,-5,NULL,1300,'H','su2','Enhanced: +100 damage (1300 damage total), better frame advantage on hit / block, and better juggle potential (even causes OTG ground bounce on airborne hits); Can only be performed during a forward jump; Puts the opponent into a limited juggle state on hit (better oki and more juggle potential than the regular OD version); Causes an OTG ground bounce on airborne hits; Forced Knockdown state while airborne; Solid hitbox for a divekick but rather slow start-up and long landing recovery frames; +10F extra recovery frames (28F) on whiff when landing behind the opponent; Crouching state on the final landing recovery frame',73,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('b8313b36-58a9-4c6e-a5c2-698ec5e22478','Mai','Kagerou no Mai','','236236P','super',6,4,59,-31,NULL,2000,'H','','Strike and Throw invincible on frames 1-8; Invincible to airborne strikes on frames 9-39; Armor Break; Depletes 0.5 Drive Bar on hit for the opponent; Grants Mai 5 Flame Stocks on the final recovery frame which enhances all her Specials as well as SA1 and SA2; Core tool in Mai''s gameplay to get her Flame Stocks; Very fast start-up for a Level 1 Super, although short range; Fantastic anti-air tool that hits on both sides of Mai; Strike hitbox that also has 8 hits of Super projectile durability; Knockdown Advantage listed refers to when used on grounded opponents (KDA is higher and varies greatly on airborne opponents)',74,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('7db0757e-fa7d-4780-9984-fdb1577f47ab','Mai','Kagerou no Mai (stock)','','236236P (stock)','normal',6,7,46,-26,NULL,2300,'H','','Enhanced: +300 damage (2300 total), better oki (KD +40 instead of +28) and increased horizontal range; Strike and Throw invincible on frames 1-6 (BUG?: 2F less invincibility than regular version); Armor Break; Depletes 0.5 Drive Bar on hit for the opponent; Grants Mai 5 Flame Stocks on the final recovery frame which enhances all her Specials as well as SA1 and SA2; Very fast start-up for a Level 1 Super, although short range; Fantastic anti-air tool that hits on both sides of Mai; Strike hitbox that also has ? hits of Super projectile durability; Knockdown Advantage listed refers to when used on grounded opponents (KDA is higher and varies greatly on airborne opponents)',75,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('eda05cf5-d93b-4958-8048-5249b878ee25','Mai','Chou Hissatsu Shinobi Bachi','','236236K','super',7,2,26,-24,NULL,2800,'H','','Fully invincible on frames 1-8; Armor Break; Depletes 1 Drive Bar on hit for the opponent; Very good range but lacks the Projectile invincibility to more easily counter projectiles, which the enhanced stock version has; Can counter projectile on reaction if close enough (can punish projectiles from much further away if you do the faster air version (Tiger Knee the QCF input)); Deals less damage at further ranges due the first few hits hitting earlier; +11F extra recovery frames (37F) on block',76,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('d072241e-6bc4-4ed1-a1a5-f095dcd0e9f3','Mai','Chou Hissatsu Shinobi Bachi (stock)','','236236K (stock)','super',7,3,31,-24,NULL,3000,'H','','Enhanced: Gains Projectile invincibility extension and +200 damage (3000 total), making this a very strong tool against other projectile users; Fully invincible on frames 1-8 and then Projectile invincible on frames 9-12; Armor Break; Depletes 1 Drive Bar on hit for the opponent; Very good range and can easily counter Projectiles on reaction (airborne version is even better at this); Deals less damage at further ranges due to first few hits hitting earlier in the active frames; +6F extra recovery frames (37F) on block',77,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('b7539878-16eb-4bd8-bb1f-18e18f5de73a','Mai','Air Chou Hissatsu Shinobi Bachi','','236236K (air)','super',3,2,24,-50,NULL,2800,'H','','No form of invincibility whatsoever; Only 3F start-up when used in air as opposed to the 7F grounded version; Armor Break; Depletes 1 Drive Bar on hit for the opponent (if all hits land); Very fast and great range makes this a good air-to-air / combo tool, and can also be used to punish long-range fireball attempts (requires good timing since projectiles can clip your hurtbox if you do it too close to the ground); Deals less damage at further ranges due to the first few hits hitting earlier in the active frames; Frame advantage and damage output varies drastically depending on distance (at least -50 on block, up to -70 or more if blocked and Mai flies over the opponent); If blocked, Mai is very likely to fly over the opponent if they''re not cornered, resulting in Mai being even more punishable on block (but potentially far away); Cannot hit cross-up (behind Mai)',78,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('4f14d51c-69ca-4515-aa79-038268cd2b16','Mai','Air Chou Hissatsu Shinobi Bachi (stock)','','236236K (stock + air)','super',3,2,24,-50,NULL,3000,'H','','Enhanced: +200 damage (3000 total); No form of invincibility whatsoever; Only 3F start-up when used in air as opposed to the 7F grounded version; Armor Break; Depletes 1 Drive Bar on hit for the opponent (if all hits land); Very fast and great range makes this a good air-to-air / combo tool, and can also be used to punish long-range fireball attempts (requires good timing since projectiles can clip your hurtbox if you do it too close to the ground); Deals less damage at further ranges due to the first few hits hitting earlier in the active frames; Frame advantage and damage output varies drastically depending on distance (at least -50 on block, up to -70 or more if blocked and Mai flies over the opponent); If blocked, Mai is very likely to fly over the opponent if they''re not cornered, resulting in Mai being even more punishable on block (but potentially far away); Cannot hit cross-up (behind Mai)',79,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('dee4a370-134e-439c-8249-a3b2bb69ae01','Mai','Shiranui Ryuu: Enbu Ada Zakura','','214214P','super',10,2,46,-33,NULL,4000,'H','','Fully invincible on frames 1-11; Armor Break; Depletes 1.5 Drive Bars on hit for the opponent; Super cinematic time regenerates ~2 Drive Bars for Mai; Only goes into the cinematic version if it hits on the first hit; Deals less damage if it doesn''t go into the cinematic version (2300~3000 damage depending on how it hits) and allows for follow-up DP juggles; 3F startup when canceled into from Hissatsu Shinobi Bachi (Cartwheel special); Incurs 50% damage scaling penalty if the non-cinematic version is used as the first hit of a combo',80,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('af54c819-594a-4b88-8792-a0bd98e4b72f','Mai','Shiranui Ryuu: Enbu Ada Zakura (Critical Art)','','214214P (CA)','super',10,2,46,-33,NULL,4500,'H','','Fully invincible on frames 1-11; Armor Break; Depletes 2 Drive Bars on hit for the opponent; Super cinematic time regenerates ~2.1 Drive Bars for Mai; Only goes into the cinematic version if it hits on the first hit; Deals less damage if it doesn''t go into the cinematic version (2300~3000 damage depending on how it hits) and allows for follow-up DP juggles; 3F startup when canceled into from Hissatsu Shinobi Bachi (Cartwheel special); Incurs 50% damage scaling penalty if the non-cinematic version is used as the first hit of a combo',81,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('4952938f-a35a-4563-a1d0-3ad61716ed06','Manon','Stand LP','','5LP','normal',4,3,10,-1,4,300,'H','ch, sp, su','Chains into stand LP / crouch LP / crouch LK; Manon''s main light combo tool since it combos naturally into QCB+LK/MK enders; Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo',1,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('08fb979e-536b-463c-ba2e-7efc40390e6e','Manon','Stand MP','','5MP','normal',7,4,15,-2,2,600,'H','sp, su, tc','Forward moving fully cancelable medium that also goes into Manon''s MP>MK target combo to get her main mixup game going; Good oki tool due to its many active frames; Punish Counter changes the properties of her target combo follow-ups',2,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('39007de0-0af8-4ea3-a88f-77e2871680dd','Manon','Stand HP','','5HP','normal',10,4,20,-3,0,800,'H','su, tc','Basically just a slower but better version of her stand MP with better damage, range, hitboxes, and target combo follow-up; Cancelable into all Super Arts; Puts airborne opponents into a limited juggle state on hit (HP follow-up pulls the opponent in with an air reset); Punish Counter changes the properties of her target combo follow-ups',3,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('24e6c9d7-1c2f-48f6-a6b1-a673685b5758','Manon','Stand LK','','5LK','normal',5,2,12,-2,2,300,'H','sp, su','Pretty decent range light button; Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo',4,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('9efe321f-cad1-44b4-be2d-fd8ed4ffe5ce','Manon','Stand MK','','5MK','normal',10,3,18,-5,-2,600,'H','sp, su','Not a low attack but is fully cancelable; Manon lifts up her front leg hurtbox on frames 9-12 (mostly during active frames) along with great hitbox priority making this a great tool against low attacks',5,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('c6dda322-fa40-4a20-be1d-c7d2c185c05e','Manon','Stand HK','','5HK','normal',15,3,26,-6,1,900,'H','','Very far range poke and punish tool (about 40% screen range) that combos into her LK/MK Dégagé (qcb+LK/MK) on Punish Counter even from max range; 3F less recovery (23F) on HIT only; Puts airborne opponents into a free juggle state on Punish Counter; The brief extended leg hurtbox on frame 14 of start-up (1F before active) is strike invincible (cannot counter-poke projectiles)',6,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('4069a172-a70b-4542-830c-a2d339371a9f','Manon','Crouch LP','','2LP','normal',4,2,11,-2,3,300,'H','ch, sp, su','Chains into stand LP / crouch LP / crouch LK; True blockstring when chained into crouch LP or stand LP; Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo; Topmost hurtboxes on frames 1-5 are vulnerable only to airborne attacks (this is to discourage its use as an anti-air)',7,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('87f55aaa-7ab7-4624-8fa6-bc8f9a96be43','Manon','Crouch MP','','2MP','normal',7,3,11,-1,6,600,'H','sp, su','+4F extra recovery frames (15F) on whiff only; Manon''s main combo starter along with back HP',8,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('29bdf9ef-01a6-47dc-a61b-ad13cef26123','Manon','Crouch HP','','2HP','normal',10,5,21,-8,-2,600,'H','tc','Manon''s extended arm and head hurtbox are invincible to airborne strikes on frames 7-34; Great anti-air tool with a built-in target combo follow-up for a KD that leaves the opponent up next to Manon for some oki',9,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('ba51126e-306b-4824-9ff4-eba3aa502448','Manon','Crouch LK','','2LK','normal',5,2,13,-3,-1,200,'L','ch','Chains into stand LP / crouch LP / crouch LK; Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo; Less pushback on hit/block compared to other light normals',10,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('422082c2-41bf-414c-b2ce-a41566b81151','Manon','Crouch MK','','2MK','normal',8,4,16,-2,3,600,'L','','A good range low poke with a ton of pushback on hit and block; Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo',11,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('10cb626e-b409-4b2d-849e-409a8aae27df','Manon','Crouch HK','','2HK','normal',11,2,27,-12,NULL,900,'L','','Standard sweep with huge range and good hitbox priority; Manon shifts forward a lot during start-up, which can push her hurtbox into a counter-poke',12,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('869d7bd5-c7a5-4d16-99db-1dc72a8bad82','Manon','Jump LP','','8LP','normal',5,10,NULL,NULL,NULL,300,'M','','',13,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('4d976731-dd96-4d2b-8401-9b95aa6de519','Manon','Jump MP','','8MP','normal',8,4,NULL,NULL,NULL,700,'M','','Fantastic air-to-air hitboxes; Puts airborne opponents into a limited juggle state; Projectile invincible on her lower body on frames 8-22 (can help Manon avoid projectiles below); Shifts the normal jumping hurtbox upward during start-up (helps with avoiding some attacks)',14,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('377fc1bc-c1a3-48f9-9d7b-01f97703581d','Manon','Jump HP','','8HP','normal',9,4,NULL,NULL,NULL,800,'M','','Spikes down airborne opponents on hit',15,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('135f0231-e98d-4ee1-aaf5-458cd2ae5992','Manon','Jump LK','','8LK','normal',6,9,NULL,NULL,NULL,300,'M','','Cross-up; Can be used as a fuzzy instant Overhead after a deep jump-in Heavy (or jump-in Mediums in Burnout as well)',16,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('2a6137eb-f24e-4a06-a5d8-177540917a72','Manon','Jump MK','','8MK','normal',7,6,NULL,NULL,NULL,500,'M','','Cross-up; Shifts the normal jumping hurtbox upward during start-up (helps with avoiding some attacks)',17,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
