('f70a6bf2-faf2-4a4c-b0aa-2f5ac96317b7','Manon','MP Manège Doré','','624MP','special',8,2,51,NULL,NULL,2000,'T','','Range: 1.37; Medium range (and medium start-up) of her command grabs; Cannot be special canceled into; Increases Manon''s Medal Level by +1 on hit; Damage and Super Gain increases with each Medal Level; Medal Level 1: 2000 damage / 3000 Super Gain; Medal Level 2: 2300 damage / 3000 Super Gain; Medal Level 3: 2700 damage / 4000 Super Gain; Medal Level 4: 3000 damage / 4000 Super Gain; Medal Level 5: 3700 damage / 5000 Super Gain',34,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
