('0ea1522b-c476-4449-b733-13f248cd132b','Marisa','Stand HK','','5HK','normal',15,2,25,-3,1,1000,'H','','Can be held; Solid poke tool with good hitbox priority that launches opponent into a free juggle state on Punish Counter; The brief extended leg hurtbox extension 1F before active frames is strike invincible (cannot counter-poke projectiles); Puts airborne opponents into a limited juggle state',7,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
