('96aec9c6-0a2a-4dd8-9b99-11cc25e9c385','Marisa','HP Phalanx','','623HP','special',32,6,15,2,NULL,1700,'H','','1 hit of armor against High and Mid attacks (loses to Low attacks) on frames 10-15; Airborne on frames 17-37 (Forced Knockdown); Low crush and lower body projectile invincible on frames 9-34; Hits 1 frame later on crouching opponents resulting in +3 on block; Causes a Hard Knockdown on Punish Counter',67,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('04d12863-ce9a-4722-ab34-b11ba4160b8f','Marisa','OD Phalanx','','623PP','special',28,6,15,4,NULL,1400,'H','','Armor Break; 1 hit of armor against High and Mid attacks (loses to Low attacks) on frames 6-12; Airborne on frames 14-33 (Forced Knockdown); Low crush and lower body projectile invincible on frames 12-30; Sends opponents tumbling backwards (can hit them OTG in this tumbling state) into a low Wall Splat state (HKD +138) if they collide with the wall; The opponent is in a grounded state during the low wall splat so they can be Thrown or Command Grabbed (but strike attacks still put the opponent into a juggle state even if they''re technically grounded); Hits 1 frame later on crouching opponents resulting in +3 on block',68,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('24a264ad-6749-484d-adc4-cb60f7eda515','Marisa','LK Quadriga','','236LK','special',20,4,24,-6,NULL,1400,'H','su3','About 50% screen length in range',69,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('0c5a978a-7bef-4951-9af9-b2b9dc2ce1b0','Marisa','MK Quadriga','','236MK','special',24,4,22,-4,NULL,1500,'H','su3','About 60% screen length in range',70,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('14340ce7-e999-48c2-99f7-734dc7248b37','Marisa','HK Quadriga','','236HK','special',29,4,21,-3,NULL,1600,'H','su3','About 70% screen length in range',71,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('ac79bfbb-463a-4747-952f-f30570b295cf','Marisa','OD Quadriga','','236KK','special',24,4,24,-6,NULL,1500,'H','su2, su3','Armor Break; Wall Splats the opponent on hit; About 65% screen length in range; KDA (Knockdown Advantage) varies between +50 (close to wall) to +68 (max range from wall) depending on distance from the wall',72,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('7f878952-9352-41a4-aeff-05a937e8e21c','Marisa','Scutum','','214K','special',3,26,26,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','1 hit of armor on frame 3 and onwards on her upper body (no armor on the lower body) while in stance (as long as the Kick button is held down) up to frame 118 (followed by 26 unarmormored recovery frames); Cancelable into follow-up attacks from frame 8; The follow-ups possible (P/K/LP+LK) are the same for both the non-OD and OD version of this stance; This stance cannot be canceled into from any other move; Marisa is in a Punish Counter state for the entire duration of this stance and all of its follow-ups; Marisa suffers a fixed 6F hitstop from any attacks that land on her armor (this can make it hard for Marisa''s counter-attack to hit the recovery frames of Mediums / Heavy attacks, resulting in a Counter-Hit instead of a Punish Counter)',73,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('5f50971d-58c4-47e2-b31c-834ca03651fd','Marisa','Scutum (absorb)','','qcb+K (absorb)','special',7,4,20,-3,-1,700,'H','','This counter-attack automatically triggers whenever Marisa''s armor during the stance absorbs any hit; No armor during the start-up of this counterattack; Armor Break (blows through all armor like Drive Impact); The counter attack advantage on hit depends on the attack that was armored; Armoring a light attack will usually result in this counter-attack to hit the recovery frames of the move, resulting in a Punish Counter for +3 frame advantage total; Armoring Medium/Heavy attacks will usually result in this counter-attack to hit the active frames of the move, resulting in a Counter-Hit for +1 frame advantage total; Holding K after the counterattack lets Marisa remain in Scutum stance; Marisa is in a Punish Counter state for the entire duration of this counterattack',74,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('b5d869db-fd7f-4d98-aac1-3d845f939626','Marisa','OD Scutum','','214KK','special',1,28,29,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','2 hits of armor on frame 1 and onward on her whole body (not just upper body like the non-OD version) while in stance (as long as a Kick buttons is held down) up to frame 58 (followed by 29 unarmored recovery frames); Cancelable into follow-up attacks from frame 8; The follow-ups possible (P/K/LP+LK) are the same for both the non-OD and OD version of this stance; This stance cannot be canceled into from any other move; Marisa is in a Punish Counter state for the entire duration of this stance and all of its follow-ups; Marisa suffers a fixed 6F hitstop from any attacks that land on her armor (this can make it hard for Marisa''s counter-attack to hit the recovery frames of Mediums / Heavy attacks, resulting in a Counter-Hit instead of a Punish Counter)',75,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('5af56e51-1ec3-4b75-90f4-354d1a8c5bb5','Marisa','OD Scutum (absorb)','','qcb+KK (absorb)','special',7,4,20,-3,-1,700,'H','','This counter-attack automatically triggers whenever Marisa''s armor during the stance absorbs any hit; 1 hit of armor on frames 1-10 (start-up and active frames); Armor Break (blows through all armor like Drive Impact); The counterattack advantage on hit depends on the attack that was armored; Armoring a light attack will usually result in this counter-attack to hit the recovery frames of the move, resulting in a Punish Counter for +3 frame advantage total; Armoring Medium/Heavy attacks will usually result in this counter-attack to hit the active frames of the move, resulting in a Counter-Hit for +1 frame advantage total; Holding K after the counterattack lets Marisa remain in Scutum stance; Marisa is in a Punish Counter state for the entire duration of this counterattack',76,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('dbd6f3f8-52ad-4b31-9126-d07bfc1616b5','Marisa','Tonitrus 1','','214K > P','special',8,3,23,-3,1,900,'M','','Overhead; First active frame can only hit airborne opponents (effectively 16F start-up against grounded opponents); Spikes down airborne opponents; +2F extra recovery frames (25F) on whiff; Marisa is in a Punish Counter state for the entire duration of this follow-up',77,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('1daff594-aa99-46be-adef-9136600ca9b0','Marisa','Tonitrus 2','','214K > P > P','special',8,3,36,-21,NULL,1900,'H','','Knocks opponent down; True blockstring; Marisa is in a Punish Counter state for the entire duration of this follow-up',78,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('e8233d5f-0fb4-405a-8ff7-7a9f7b5b7492','Marisa','Procella','','214K > K','special',8,3,37,-24,NULL,1200,'L','','Low; Hard Knockdown; Marisa is in a Punish Counter state for the entire duration of this follow-up',79,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('980dfe41-0541-4285-b1d5-91f3dfcd02fb','Marisa','Enfold','','214K > LPLK','special',8,3,54,NULL,NULL,2500,'T','','Range: 1.11~1.17; Minimum start-up overall is 13F if you factor in the 8F start-up of the stance before the 5F command grab is initiated; Marisa is in a Punish Counter state for the entire duration of this follow-up',80,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('e0e3aee8-0ff7-499b-9fcb-3ae7899809ea','Marisa','Javelin of Marisa','','236236P','super',19,5,60,-43,NULL,2200,'H','','Strike and Throw invincible on frame 1 (during screen freeze); 2 hits of armor on frames 1-23; Armor Break; Depletes 0.5 Drive Bar on hit for the opponent; Performs the cinematic counter if any Punch is held if Marisa is hit during the armor frames (KD +46)',81,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('5977de5a-f934-4ec4-980a-9f20a7e8652a','Marisa','Javelin of Marisa (Hold)','','236236P (hold)','super',42,6,60,-42,NULL,2900,'H','','Strike and Throw invincible on frame 1 (during screen freeze); 2 hits of armor on frames 1-47; Armor Break; Depletes 0.75 Drive Bar on hit for the opponent; Only triggers cinematic punch on first 3 active frames; Cannot trigger the cinematic punch when hitting OTG; Non-cinematic punch on remaining active frames deals 300 less damage (2600) and is only KD +17; Triggers a cinematic counter if the armor absorbs a strike or throw on frames 2-27 (projectiles do not trigger this)',82,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('211e5d6c-49a4-4299-833c-00f625ea68cb','Marisa','Javelin of Marisa (Counter)','','236236P (counter)','super',6,3,54,-37,NULL,2400,'H','','Fully invincible on frames 1-10; Armor Break; Depletes 0.5 Drive Bar on hit for the opponent; This counterattack only activates if the armor absorbs a strike or throw on frames 2-27 on the held version of this Super',83,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('29c35e3a-cc35-4f12-b532-8e7b749f629b','Marisa','Meteorite','','214214P','super',9,8,59,-44,NULL,3000,'H','','Fully invincible on frames 1-16; Airborne on frames 17-47 (Forced Knockdown); Armor Break; Depletes 1 Drive Bar on hit for the opponent; Also functions as an anti-air; If the first hit doesn''t go into the cinematic finish (on block or whiff), then Marisa comes down with a second swing that deals 500 less damage (2500) by itself; Block/Parry data shown in parentheses (X) refers to when only the first hit is blocked/parried (can jump afterwards to avoid the second hit); Can be steered by holding forward or back, giving it more range on startup or making it less likely to whiff against cross-ups',84,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('881aad72-73ff-4e48-9a5f-2639c04dca23','Marisa','Goddess of the Hunt','','236236K','super',13,7,60,-39,NULL,4000,'H','','Fully invincible on frames 1-19; Armor Break; Depletes 2 Drive Bars on hit for the opponent; Super cinematic time regenerates ~2.1 Drive Bars for Marisa; Very far range for a Super makes this an excellent Punish tool in many scenarios (extra scary with Modern controls); Carries the opponent to the corner no matter where it hits on screen',85,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('e6650df7-ffdc-4faf-a835-0abb31581396','Marisa','Goddess of the Hunt (Critical Art)','','236236K (CA)','super',13,7,60,-39,NULL,4500,'H','','Fully invincible on frames 1-19; Armor Break; Critical Art does +500 extra damage over regular version; Armor Break; Depletes 2 Drive Bars on hit for the opponent; Super cinematic time regenerates ~2.1 Drive Bars for Marisa; Very far range for a Super makes this an excellent Punish tool in many scenarios (extra scary with Modern controls); Carries the opponent to the corner no matter where it hits on screen',86,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('04fa772d-289f-4901-8ed5-2b7bb4cfdf52','Rashid','Stand LP','','5LP','normal',4,2,9,-1,4,300,'H','ch, sp, su','Chains into stand LP / crouch LP / crouch LK; Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo',1,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('b12a3db4-891a-46da-a103-0de2359f40e4','Rashid','Stand MP','','5MP','normal',6,3,14,1,5,600,'H','tc, sp, su','Rashid''s main combo tool',2,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('ea69c4a3-6fff-48d3-a3e0-3ce1cf11f788','Rashid','Stand HP','','5HP','normal',9,3,21,-4,1,800,'H','sp, su','Decent poke tool that''s fully cancelable',3,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('d2df5867-66df-42f8-8c11-7eb8d553b7a8','Rashid','Stand LK','','5LK','normal',4,3,10,-1,3,300,'H','sp, su','Has slightly higher hitstun than Rashid''s other light attacks, making this the only light that can naturally combo into LK Eagle Spike (QCB+LK); Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo',4,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('488dcb85-99ca-426a-a355-703765cc9ffa','Rashid','Stand MK','','5MK','normal',8,3,17,-3,6,600,'H','','Mostly a combo tool (links into stand MP); Decent poke that combos into itself on Counter-Hit; Has +2 extra recovery frames (19F) on whiff',5,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('18f10246-2d12-4c11-833a-ef533afdaf71','Rashid','Stand HK','','5HK','normal',13,8,18,-5,-1,800,'H','','Combo / Juggle tool with surprisingly far range; Launches airborne opponents into a limited juggle state (launches grounded opponents as well on Punish Counter and pulls the opponent towards Rashid for easier follow-ups); Cannot hit cross-up (behind Rashid); Can be used as an oki / meaty tool, but has a lot of pushback on hit and block; Forces stand on hit; The brief extended leg hurtbox extension on frame 12 (1F before active) is strike invincible (cannot counter-poke projectiles); Last 2 active frames whiff on crouch',6,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('155bc3d9-2c64-4a04-adb6-5fb0812862b6','Rashid','Crouch LP','','2LP','normal',5,3,7,-1,5,300,'H','ch, sp, su','Chains into stand LP / crouch LP / crouch LK; Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo; Topmost hurtboxes on frames 1-7 are vulnerable only to airborne attacks (this is to discourage its use as an anti-air)',7,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('a5941813-4e73-4697-9127-22300e9fc4ab','Rashid','Crouch MP','','2MP','normal',6,4,13,1,4,600,'H','sp, su','Rashid''s main frametrap / oki / combo tool as well as being a decent anti-air on frames 7-9; Cannot hit cross-up (behind Rashid); Whiffs on crouching from further away',8,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('b7f30c2a-ff93-43be-9fb6-7a927eb0ae9a','Rashid','Crouch HP','','2HP','normal',12,3,21,-6,5,900,'H','su','Decent poke / punish tool that''s cancelable into all Super Arts and combos into stand HP on Punish Counter (if close enough to the opponent); A lot of pushback on hit and block; Incurs 20% hit damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo; Has +2 extra recovery frames (23F) on whiff',9,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('5edefd04-dc0e-4aaa-bae1-a45e6be82359','Rashid','Crouch LK','','2LK','normal',5,3,8,-1,3,200,'L','ch','Chains into stand LP / crouch LP / crouch LK; Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo',10,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('caf0ae93-6c8d-424b-8bb1-92c7811d2de0','Rashid','Crouch MK','','2MK','normal',7,3,18,-5,-1,500,'L','sp, su','Standard crouch MK with a bit short range; Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo',11,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('409c45ca-e780-46ef-88bc-a1e0d50a194d','Rashid','Crouch HK','','2HK','normal',9,3,24,-11,NULL,900,'L','','Has some Juggle potential naturally without Drive Rush; Has fixed framedata on block (always -11 on block even if blocked meaty) with +4F extra recovery frames (28F)',12,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
