('727a120f-1cbd-456c-89ea-8acd33cc6b23','Rashid','Rising Kick','','5MP > 5HK','normal',13,4,36,-20,NULL,400,'H','sp, su','Launches the opponent into a limited juggle state on hit; Fully cancelable on hit and block; Counts as 2 hits of damage scaling',28,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('05236dfe-cb11-4cd1-970b-aa4063aadc04','Rashid','Side Flip','','6KK','unique',NULL,NULL,32,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','Rashid flips forward with no collision boxes on frames 8-23 allowing him to flip through opponents; Rashid can follow-up the flip with 3 different jump trajectories on frames 19-25; Wind enhancement on frames 2-20: Almost full-screen range flip',29,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('5e5d295c-3473-4c99-a01c-4b3ebc4abff8','Rashid','Front Flip','','6KK > 4 or 5 or 6KK','unique',NULL,NULL,8,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','Trajectory of the jump depends on which direction is held while inputting KK; Back: Short jump trajectory; Neutral: Far jump trajectory (bit further than regular forward jump); Forward: Extra far jump trajectory (goes past the opponent mid-screen); Can use any air attack on frames 22-40; 8F landing recovery frames if no air attack in input; Wind enhancement on frames 1-36: All flips go full-screen forward',30,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('986d570f-8787-4a65-91e1-33d17411a84f','Rashid','Wall Jump','','9 or 3 (near wall)','unique',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','Forced Knockdown and Counter-Hit state for the entire duration of the jump; Can be performed after any jump direction as long as the wall is in range; Cannot be peformed after Blitz Strike (d+HP in air) or Arabian Skyhigh (QCB+K in air)',31,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('4e4e1786-fb43-41da-95af-9c973469a5c8','Rashid','Riding Glider','','LPLK','throw',5,3,23,NULL,NULL,1200,'T','','Throw Loop: hold Run briefly, then stop for a manually timed strike/throw mixup (does not work on mid-screen back rolls); Throw Loop has a 3F timing window (4F on Blanka / E. Honda / Zangief); Gets +70% damage increase (2040 damage), HKD (denies back-roll option on wake-up), and depletes 1 bar of Drive Gauge on a Punish Counter',32,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('2316c387-5bb4-4ae5-acee-06e2b8821e7b','Rashid','Sunset Drop','','4LPLK','throw',5,3,23,NULL,NULL,1200,'T','','Throw Oki: Can Drive Rush into a meaty strike; Gets +70% damage increase (2040 damage), HKD (denies back-roll option on wake-up), and depletes 1 bar of Drive Gauge on a Punish Counter',33,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
