('99c212ab-837e-4cfc-903c-996cf5dcc116','Ryu','Stand HP','','5HP','normal',10,5,18,-2,4,800,'H','sp, su','Fantastic combo / poke tool that''s hit confirmable with a lot of active frames; Forces stand (vital for the HP > HK target combo follow-up); Shoto stand HP privilege',3,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('6013dd0d-e1f4-4e75-9489-4a611a760f8b','Ryu','Stand LK','','5LK','normal',5,3,11,-4,2,300,'H','sp, su','Good range for a light normal; Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo',4,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('d4fb349d-93b3-4589-b086-d64e182f026a','Ryu','Stand MK','','5MK','normal',9,3,18,-4,4,700,'H','','Good poke tool with good hitbox priority (disjoint); Ryu lifts up his front leg hurtbox on frames 4-11 making this a good tool against low attacks',5,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('4cac3acf-75f4-4d58-b430-66caa2e82f01','Ryu','Stand HK','','5HK','normal',12,4,20,1,9,900,'H','','Whiffs on most crouching moves (can still hit some like crouch HP); Good horizontal anti-air; Puts airborne opponents into a juggle state; Crumples on Punish Counter (+11 frames before the crumple state goes airborne); The brief extended leg hurtbox on frame 11 of start-up (1F before active) is strike invincible (cannot counter-poke projectiles)',6,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('b7b7278c-b058-4c0c-9653-dc8401f4cad4','Ryu','Crouch LP','','2LP','normal',4,2,9,-1,4,300,'H','ch, sp, su','Chains into stand LP / crouch LP / crouch LK; Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo; Topmost hurtboxes on frames 1-5 are vulnerable only to airborne attacks (this is to discourage its use as an anti-air)',7,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('c7d118fc-7d17-4789-b413-72416db39312','Ryu','Crouch MP','','2MP','normal',6,4,13,0,5,600,'H','sp, su','Great combo / poke / buffer / pressure tool; 4 active frames and solid frame advantage makes this an ideal oki tool as well; +2F extra recovery frames (15F) on whiff only; Topmost hurtboxes on frames 1-9 are vulnerable only to airborne attacks (this is to discourage its use as an anti-air)',8,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('76f0b7e4-d10c-4ded-b1e7-452545af899d','Ryu','Crouch HP','','2HP','normal',9,6,21,-7,1,800,'H','sp, su','Extended fist hurtbox is invincible to airborne strikes on frame 9; Head hurtbox is invincible to airborne strikes on frames 10-14; Forces stand on hit; Solid anti-air; Cannot hit cross-up (behind Ryu); Only cancelable on the first active frame; Deals 5F less hitstun after the first active frame resulting in worse frame advantage on hit beyond the first active frame (can''t get any meaty combos on oki)',9,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('df4acd99-9c85-411c-b0f0-b3de70f011bf','Ryu','Crouch LK','','2LK','normal',5,2,10,-1,3,200,'L','ch','Chains into stand LP / crouch LP / crouch LK; Incurs 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo',10,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('2e573c9c-5cc9-4ae2-bb9a-b5c9f64d0adc','Ryu','Crouch MK','','2MK','normal',8,3,19,-6,1,500,'L','sp, su','Standard shoto crouch MK; If blocked, Ryu can safely cancel into Hadoken while recovering in time to counter Drive Impact; Incurs a 20% damage scaling penalty if used as the first hit of a combo; Footsies!',11,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('59467fe9-ff9b-42da-9796-e1a4df8c46a0','Ryu','Crouch HK','','2HK','normal',9,3,23,-12,NULL,900,'L','','Has very good range and hitbox priority; Has some Juggle potential naturally without Drive Rush; Has fixed framedata on block (always -12 on block even if blocked meaty) with +6F extra recovery frames (29F)',12,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('de0703bb-730c-42ce-a8db-10ddd974c75f','Ryu','Jump LP','','8LP','normal',4,10,NULL,0,4,300,'M','','Can be used as a fuzzy instant Overhead after a deep jump-in Medium / Heavy',13,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('a110b6df-cccf-4059-acb5-70bba663dadd','Ryu','Jump MP','','8MP','normal',8,2,NULL,7,11,700,'M','sp','Both hits put airborne opponents into a limited juggle state; Both hits are cancelable into Air Tatsus; Great air-to-air hitbox priority; Shifts the normal jumping hurtbox upward during start-up (helps with avoiding some attacks)',14,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
