('a8f86de1-f1d9-45bf-bc9a-ebe8806f29b6','Ryu','HK High Blade Kick','','236HK','special',27,9,15,-3,NULL,1300,'H','su3','Launches opponent into a limited juggle state on hit (allows corner juggle into LP/MP/OD Shoryuken or Lv.3 Super); Launches opponent into a tumbling OTG state on Punish Counter; Has huge range, a deceptively large hitbox, tons of active frames, and huge pushback on block; Huge cancel window makes this easy to hit confirm into SA3 (also allows Ryu to punish the opponent if they absorb it with Drive Impact)',53,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('21399d04-77b6-4c13-a400-c53a1acaa67c','Ryu','OD High Blade Kick','','236KK','special',17,5,33,-18,NULL,800,'H','su2, su3','Launches opponent into a wall bounce on hit; Incurs 5% damage scaling penalty to the next hit when used in the middle of a combo; Very lenient cancel window makes this relatively easy to hit confirm into SA3',54,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
('40ef167c-dc02-4603-9598-1b484abc0ce5','Ryu','LP Hashogeki','','214LP','special',12,6,18,-3,2,700,'H','su3','Strike hitbox but has 1-hit of projectile durability against non-OD projectiles (OD projectiles still break through it); Puts airborne opponents into a limited juggle state on hit; Launches opponent into a spinning juggle state on Counter Hit and Punish Counter; Safe and minimal pushback on block makes this a great tool oki tool when used meaty (up to +7/+2 on last active frame)',55,datetime('now'),datetime('now')),
